%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dollarization%20is%20the%20only%20way%20for%20Argentina%20to%20stop%20its%20'death%20spiral'%2C%20economist%20Steve%20Hanke%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223560%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Argentine%20peso%20bills%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f087faf8c8620019614866%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222670%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3E(Photo%20by%20LEO%20LA%20VALLE%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERed-hot%20inflation%20and%20a%20plunging%20peso%20have%20fueled%20calls%20for%20Argentina%20to%20ditch%20its%20currency.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EEconomist%20Steve%20Hanke%20reiterated%20his%20view%20that%20the%20country%20should%20adopt%20the%20dollar%20as%20the%20means%20of%20exchange.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BDOLLARIZATION%20is%20the%20only%20way%20to%20stop%20Argentina's%20death%20spiral%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAdopting%20the%20dollar%20as%20currency%20is%20the%20only%20way%20for%20Argentina%20to%20stop%20the%20%26quot%3Bdeath%20spiral%26quot%3B%20engulfing%20its%20economy%2C%20according%20to%20economist%20Steve%20Hanke.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Johns%20Hopkins%20professor%20echoed%20the%20views%20of%20Argentina's%20presidential%20candidate%20Javier%20Milei%20%E2%80%93%20who%20has%20also%20called%20for%20ditching%20the%20peso%20and%20adopting%20the%20greenback%20as%20a%20way%20to%20tame%20rampant%20inflation%20in%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20economic%20model%20championed%20by%20former%20Argentine%20ruler%20Juan%20Peron%2C%20and%20followed%20by%20later%20rulers%2C%20has%20left%20the%20economy%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsteve_hanke%2Fstatus%2F1697421408177992116%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eteetering%20on%20the%20brink%20of%20collapse%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20Hanke%20wrote%20in%20a%20Thursday%20post%20on%20X.%20He%20measures%20the%20South%20American%20nation's%20current%20annual%20inflation%20rate%20at%20more%20than%20160%25%2C%20way%20above%20the%20official%20print%20of%20113%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPres.%20Fernandez's%20disastrous%20Peronista%20policies%20have%20left%20Argentina's%20economy%20in%20shambles%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsteve_hanke%2Fstatus%2F1696978847290544197%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20post%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Wednesday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20I%20measure%20inflation%20in%20ARG%20at%20166%25%2Fyr.%20DOLLARIZATION%20is%20the%20only%20way%20to%20stop%20Argentina's%20death%20spiral.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20months%20now%2C%20Hanke%20has%20been%20a%20consistent%20advocate%20of%20Argentina%20adopting%20the%20greenback.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fdollarization-only-way-out-argentina-debt-trap-steve-hanke-2023-7%3Futm_medium%3Dingest%26utm_source%3Dmarkets%5C%22%3EHe%20said%20in%20July%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20dollarization%20is%20Argentina's%20only%20way%20out%20of%20its%20deepening%20debt%20trap%20and%20suggested%20%26quot%3Bmothballing%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fdollarization-argentina-mothball-central-bank-dollarize-peso-inflation-steve-hanke-2023-8%5C%22%3Eits%20central%20bank%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Argentine%20peso%20has%20collapsed%20in%20value%20over%20the%20past%20decade%20as%20the%20nation%20struggled%20with%20hyperinflation%20and%20a%20mountain%20of%20borrowing.%20Its%20external%20debt%20ballooned%20to%2045%25%20of%20its%20GDP%20at%20the%20end%20of%202022%2C%20standing%20at%20%24277%20billion%2C%20according%20to%20CEIC%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20currency%20crisis%20has%20largely%20been%20fueled%20by%20a%20shortage%20of%20the%20US%20dollar%2C%20forcing%20Argentina's%20commercial%20banks%20to%20set%20up%20deposit%20accounts%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fdollarization-only-way-out-argentina-debt-trap-steve-hanke-2023-7%3Futm_medium%3Dingest%26utm_source%3Dmarkets%5C%22%3Ein%20the%20Chinese%20yuan%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20shortage%20was%20caused%20by%20an%20ongoing%20drought%20that%20struck%20the%20country's%20agricultural%20exports%2C%20depleting%20the%20central%20bank's%20dollar%20reserves%20to%20their%20lowest%20level%20since%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECalls%20for%20increased%20use%20of%20the%20US%20dollar%20would%20undermine%20'dedollarization'%20attempts%20by%20the%20South%20American%20nation.%20Argentina%20had%20previously%20sought%20to%20wean%20itself%20off%20the%20greenback%20in%20the%20same%20way%20as%20China%2C%20India%2C%20and%20Brazil%20have%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdollarization-only-way-out-of-argentinas-death-spiral-steve-hanke-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693556350000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f087faf8c8620019614863%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fdollarization-only-way-out-of-argentinas-death-spiral-steve-hanke-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Johns%20Hopkins%20professor%20echoed%20the%20views%20of%20Argentina's%20presidential%20candidate%20Javier%20Milei%20%E2%80%93%20who%20has%20also%20called%20for%20adopting%20the%20greenback%20as%20the%20country's%20local%20currency.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jwilkins%40insider.com%20(Joseph%20Wilkins)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fdollarization-only-way-out-of-argentinas-death-spiral-steve-hanke-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%2