%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Flaw-today%2Fstory%2Fdeath-row-convict-cant-appeal-against-presidents-mercy-plea-order-bnss-bill-2429274-2023-08-31%5C%22%3Eread%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20ruled%20in%20the%20past%20that%20the%20exercise%20of%20prerogative%20powers%2C%20such%20as%20clemency%20and%20pardons%2C%20by%20the%20president%20or%20the%20governor%20may%20be%20challenged%20in%20court.%20In%20some%20cases%2C%20like%20that%20of%20Mumbai%20blast%20convict%20Yakub%20Memon%20and%20in%20the%20Nirbhaya%20case%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Flaw-today%2Fstory%2Fdeath-row-convict-cant-appeal-against-presidents-mercy-plea-order-bnss-bill-2429274-2023-08-31%5C%22%3Edeath%20row%20convicts%20approached%20the%20court%20at%20the%2011th%20hour%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20seeking%20a%20review%20of%20the%20president%E2%80%99s%20rejection%20of%20their%20mercy%20petitions.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20refused%20to%20stay%20the%20executions%20in%20both%20the%20cases.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20new%20bill%20also%20seeks%20to%20avoid%20a%20delay%20on%20account%20of%20separate%20pleas%20filed%20by%20multiple%20convicts%20in%20the%20same%20case%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20the%20proposed%20Bill%2C%20a%20jail%20superintendent%20shall%20ensure%20that%20every%20convict%2C%20in%20case%20there%20are%20more%20than%20one%20in%20a%20case%2C%20submits%20the%20mercy%20plea%20within%2060%20days%20and%20where%20no%20such%20petition%20is%20received%20from%20the%20other%20convicts%2C%20he%20shall%20himself%20send%20the%20names%2C%20addresses%2C%20copies%20of%20the%20case%20records%20and%20all%20other%20details%20to%20the%20Union%20or%20the%20state%20government%2C%20along%20with%20the%20original%20mercy%20petition%2C%20the%20report%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Flaw-today%2Fstory%2Fdeath-row-convict-cant-appeal-against-presidents-mercy-plea-order-bnss-bill-2429274-2023-08-31%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20president%20shall%20decide%20the%20petitions%20of%20all%20the%20convicts%20together.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EApart%20from%20specifying%20time-limits%20for%20filing%20mercy%20pleas%20in%20death-row%20cases%20with%20the%20governor%20(Article%20161)%20and%20the%20president%20(Article%2072)%2C%20section%20473%20of%20the%20BNSS%20Bill%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Flaw-today%2Fstory%2Fdeath-row-convict-cant-appeal-against-presidents-mercy-plea-order-bnss-bill-2429274-2023-08-31%5C%22%3Eseeks%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20give%20the%20Union%2060%20days%E2%80%99%20time%20from%20the%20date%20of%20receipt%20of%20the%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20comments%20on%20the%20pleas%20to%20send%20its%20recommendation%20to%20the%20president.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20no%20time-limit%20has%20been%20specified%20for%20the%20president%20for%20disposing%20of%20the%20mercy%20petitions%2C%20the%20president%E2%80%99s%20decision%20on%20such%20a%20plea%20is%20sought%20to%20be%20communicated%20by%20the%20Union%20to%20the%20state%20home%20department%20and%20jail%20superintendent%20concerned%20within%2048%20hours%20of%20the%20disposal%2C%20the%20report%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Flaw-today%2Fstory%2Fdeath-row-convict-cant-appeal-against-presidents-mercy-plea-order-bnss-bill-2429274-2023-08-31%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693554356000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F05%2F12171900%2FPrison-bars.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fnew-bill-proposes-to-make-presidents-call-on-mercy-plea-final-to-reduce-judicial-delays%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20ruled%20in%20the%20past%20that%20the%20exercise%20of%20prerogative%20powers%2C%20such%20as%20clemency%20and%20pardons%2C%20by%20the%20president%20or%20the%20governor%20may%20be%20challenged%20in%20court.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fnew-bill-proposes-to-make-presidents-call-on-mercy-plea-final-to-reduce-judicial-delays%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BPlaying%20India%20In%20Ahmedabad...%26quot%3B%3A%20Sourav%20Ganguly%20Fires%20Warning%20To%20Pakistan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20Pakistan%20are%20set%20for%20some%20enthralling%20cricketing%20battles%20on%20the%2022-yard%20strip%2C%20with%20the%20two%20Asian%20giants%20set%20to%20face%20each%20other%20on%20multiple%20occasions%20in%20the%20coming%20months.%20With%20three%20matches%20in%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20likely%2C%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20are%20also%20scheduled%20to%20clash%20in%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20next%20month.%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sourav%20Ganguly%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F197-sourav-ganguly-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESourav%20Ganguly%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20former%20India%20skipper%2C%20doesn't%20agree%20with%20certain%20players'%20suggestion%20that%20it%20is%20'just%20another%20game'%2C%20and%20wants%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E's%20men%20to%20be%20fully%20prepared.%20While%20Paksitan%20do%20have%20a%20top%20team%2C%20Ganguly%20doesn't%20feel%20playing%20India%20in%20Ahmedabad%20on%20the%20World%20Cup%20stage%20will%20be%20as%20easy%20for%20them%20as%20it%20seems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20huge%20game.%20Always%20was%20and%20always%20will%20be.%20You%20have%20realised%20how%20important%20it%20is%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20World%20Cup.%20I%20used%20to%20treat%20it%20very%20much%20like%20an%20India%20Australia%2C%20India%20South%20Africa%20contest.%20I%20used%20to%20get%20into%20the%20mindset%20that%20it%20is%20still%20the%20red%20ball%20or%20the%20white%20ball%20you%20are%20up%20against%20and%20prepare%20myself%20like%20that.%20You%20can't%20let%20the%20occasion%20get%20to%20you%20because%20that's%20when%20you%20tend%20to%20lose%20focus%2C%26quot%3B%20Ganguly%20said%20in%20a%20chat%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frevsportz.in%2Fdont-keep-chopping-and-changing-till-the-last-minute-settled-combination-key-to-winning-a-world-cup-sourav-ganguly%2F%5C%22%3ERevSportz%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20its%20not%20just%20another%20game.%20You%20have%20to%20prepare%20yourself%20that%20way.%20That's%20how%20you%20manage%20pressure.%20Some%20manage%20and%20some%20don't%20manage.%20In%20my%20tenure%20we%20had%20a%20great%20record%20against%20Pakistan%20but%20this%20time%20round%20it%20will%20be%20a%20more%20competitive%20game.%20Last%20year%20after%20Pakistan%20beat%20India%20in%20Dubai%20things%20have%20changed.%20Pakistan%20is%20also%20a%20very%20good%20side%20and%20it%20is%20amazing%20how%20they%20keep%20churning%20out%20extraordinary%20talent.%20But%20playing%20India%20in%20India%2C%20playing%20India%20in%20Ahmedabad%20and%20playing%20India%20in%20front%20of%20110%2C000%20fans%20is%20very%20different%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGanguly%20also%20explained%20his%20earlier%20statement%2C%20suggesting%20India%20will%20not%20win%20all%20the%20finals.%20The%20former%20BCCI%20president%20said%20that%20the%20team%20needs%20to%20focus%20on%20small%20milestones%20first.%20To%20win%20a%20final%2C%20first%20they%20have%20to%20reach%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSaying%20that%20India%20will%20not%20always%20win%20finals%2C%20he%20went%20on%20to%20say%2C%20'You%20won't%20win%20all%20finals'.%20But%20then%20you%20need%20to%20make%20it%20to%20the%20final%20first.%20So%20you%20need%20to%20break%20things%20down.%20First%20you%20need%20to%20play%20well%20and%20win%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20nine%20games%20to%20be%20able%20to%20make%20the%20final.%20Don't%20think%20about%20the%20final%20at%20the%20start%20of%20the%20tournament.%20It%20is%20much%20like%20batting.%20When%20you%20go%20into%20bat%20don't%20think%20of%20the%20100.%20Get%20to%2050%2C%2060%2C%2070%20and%20then%20when%20you%20get%20to%2090%20that's%20when%20you%20think%20of%20the%20100.%20For%20the%20World%20Cup%20it%20is%20the%20same.%20First%20play%20well%20and%20get%20to%20the%20final.%20Once%20you%20are%20there%20that's%20when%20you%20plan%20for%20the%20final%20and%20try%20and%20win%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Dada%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693554000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2Fksaptkhg_sourav-ganguly-bcci_625x300_10_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fplaying-india-in-ahmedabad-sourav-ganguly-fires-world-cup-warning-to-pakistan-4347250%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indian%20cricket%20legend%20Sourav%20Ganguly%20has%20fired%20a%20firm%20warning%20to%20Pakistan%20over%20World%20Cup%20clash%20against%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fplaying-india-in-ahmedabad-sourav-ganguly-fires-world-cup-warning-to-pakistan-4347250%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fplaying-india-in-ahmedabad-sourav-ganguly-fires-world-cup-warning-to-pakistan-4347250%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fplaying-india-in-ahmedabad-sourav-ganguly-fires-world-cup-warning-to-pakistan-4347250%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Realness%20Institute%20Spotlights%20African%20Talent%20at%20FAME%20Week%20(EXCLUSIVE)%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693553753000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.c