alUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ftorrent-pharma-gears-up-to-buyout-cipla-promoters-approach-pe-funding-123090100398_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ftorrent-pharma-gears-up-to-buyout-cipla-promoters-approach-pe-funding-123090100398_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ftorrent-pharma-gears-up-to-buyout-cipla-promoters-approach-pe-funding-123090100398_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explained%3A%20What%20'One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election'%20Means%20And%20Why%20It's%20Being%20Done%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20Central%20government%20has%20constituted%20a%20panel%C2%A0to%20explore%20the%20possibility%20of%20'One%20Nation%20One%20Election'%20in%20the%20country.%20A%20notification%20about%20the%20members%20of%20the%20panel%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbig-move-on-one-nation-one-election-panel-formed-to-explore-possibility-4347165%5C%22%3Eheaded%20by%20former%20President%20Ram%20Nath%20Kovind%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20issued%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThis%20comes%20alongside%20a%20special%20Parliament%20session%20called%20by%20the%20government%20from%20September%2018%20to%2022.%20The%20surprise%20announcement%20of%20the%20session%20has%20led%20to%20speculations%20that%20the%20government%20is%20planning%20to%20introduce%20a%20bill%20on%20%26quot%3BOne%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20concept%20refers%20to%20holding%20simultaneous%20polls%20across%20the%20country.%20The%20proposal%20is%20to%20conduct%20elections%20for%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20all%20state%20assemblies%20at%20the%20same%20time.%20In%20India%2C%20the%20general%20elections%20to%20elect%20the%20members%20of%20Parliament%20and%20state%20assembly%20polls%20are%20held%20separately%20when%20the%20tenure%20of%20the%20incumbent%20government%20comes%20to%20an%20end%20or%20it%20gets%20dissolved%20for%20some%20reason.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Positives%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20been%20advocating%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentres-one-nation-one-election-proposal-is-unconstitutional-aap-3718390%5C%22%3EOne%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election%3C%2Fa%3E%20idea%20for%20a%20long%20time%20now.%20In%20fact%2C%20it%20was%20one%20of%20the%20components%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party's%20election%20manifesto%20for%20the%202014%20Lok%20Sabha%20Polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20supporters%20of%20'One%20Nation%20One%20Election'%20often%20underline%20that%20once%20implemented%2C%20it%20would%20bring%20down%20the%20overall%20expenditure%20on%20the%20electoral%20process.%20With%20so%20many%20states%2C%20there's%20always%20an%20election%20in%20some%20or%20the%20other%20part%20of%20the%20country%2C%20leading%20to%20excessive%20expenditure%20in%20the%20process%20both%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI)%20and%20contestants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20argument%20favouring%20the%20One%20Nation%20One%20Election%20is%20that%20it%20will%20lead%20to%20a%20more%20efficient%20administration.%20During%20elections%2C%20the%20entire%20state%20machinery%20focuses%20on%20conducting%20a%20free%20and%20fair%20electoral%20process%2C%20which%20impacts%20the%20everyday%20administration%20because%20officials%20are%20engaged%20in%20polling%20duties.%20Simultaneous%20elections%20will%20likely%20boost%20voter%20turnout%2C%20making%20it%20convenient%20for%20the%20electorate%20to%20cast%20the%20ballot%20at%20once.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbig-move-on-one-nation-one-election-panel-formed-to-explore-possibility-4347165%5C%22%3EOne%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20expected%20to%20bring%20consistency%20and%20continuity%20in%20policies%20and%20programmes%20of%20the%20Central%20government%20and%20states.%20During%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20once%20the%20model%20code%20of%20conduct%20is%20enforced%2C%20no%20state%20can%20launch%20new%20projects%20or%20schemes%20until%20the%20polls%20are%20concluded.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChallenges%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20challenge%20in%20the%20way%20of%20the%20'One%20Nation%20One%20election'%20is%20to%20sync%20the%20terms%20of%20the%20various%20state%20legislative%20assemblies%20with%20those%20of%20Lok%20Sabha.%20There%20is%20also%20no%20clarity%20on%20dealing%20with%20situations%20like%20midterm%20polls%20or%20the%20President's%20rule%20in%20case%20any%20party%20fails%20to%20get%20the%20majority.%20Regional%20political%20parties%20argue%20that%20having%20the%20two%20elections%20simultaneously%20would%20hamper%20their%20prospects%20because%20they%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20highlight%20local%20issues%20prominently.%20Furthermore%2C%20they%20fear%20they%20can't%20compete%20with%20national%20parties%20in%20money%20and%20election%20strategies%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693553460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-11%2Fmpbfnv4_election-generic-afp650_625x300_02_November_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-what-one-nation-one-election-means-and-why-its-being-done-4347498%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Central%20government%20has%20constituted%20a%20panel%2C%20headed%20by%20former%20President%20Ram%20Nath%20Kovind%2C%20to%20explore%20the%20possibility%20of%20'One%20Nation%20One%20Election'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-what-one-nation-one-election-means-and-why-its-being-done-4347498%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-what-one-nation-one-election-means-and-why-its-being-done-4347498%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-what-one-nation-one-election-means-and-why-its-being-done-4347498%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Man%20Has%20Survived%20For%2070%20Years%20After%20Being%20Struck%20Down%20By%20Polio%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20man%20in%20the%20US%20has%20spent%20more%20than%20seven%20decades%20inside%20a%20600-pound%20iron%20lung%20after%20being%20struck%20down%20by%20polio%20at%20the%20age%20of%20six.%20Paul%20Alexander%20has%20been%20paralysed%20from%20the%20neck%20down%20since%201952%20due%20to%20the%20disease%2C%20leaving%20him%20unable%20to%20breathe%20by%20himself.%20According%20to%20%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%26quot%3BPolio%20Paul%26quot%3B%20has%20refused%20to%20upgrade%20to%20a%20modern%20machine.%20In%20March%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.guinnessworldrecords.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F3%2Fmeet-longest-surviving-iron-lung-patient-kept-alive-by-a-machine-for-70-years-741881%5C%22%3EGuinness%20World%20Records%20(GWR)%3C%2Fa%3E%20declared%20the%2077-year-old%20as%20the%20longest%20iron%20lung%20patient%20ever.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Alexander%20has%20faced%20many%20challenges%20since%20he%20was%20born%20in%201946.%20He%20endured%20the%20worst%20polio%20outbreak%20in%20US%20history%20with%20almost%2058%2C000%20cases%20-%20mostly%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2023%2F08%2F31%2Fhow-polio-paul-survived-living-in-an-iron-lung-for-70-years%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EPost%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20disease%20severely%20affected%20Mr%20Alexander%2C%20requiring%20him%20to%20use%20a%20machine%20to%20breathe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolion%2C%20or%20Poliomyelitis%2C%20is%20a%20disabling%20and%20life-threatening%20disease%20caused%20by%20the%20poliovirus.%20The%20virus%20spreads%20from%20person%20to%20person%20and%20can%20infect%20a%20person's%20spinal%20cord%2C%20causing%20paralysis.%20It%20made%20Mr%20Alexander%20too%20weak%20to%20breathe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20polio%20vaccine%20was%20approved%20and%20widely%20administered%20to%20children%20across%20the%20US%20in%201955.%20The%20country%20was%20declared%20polio%20free%20in%201979%2C%20but%20it%20was%20too%20late%20for%20Mr%20Alexander%20by%20that%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20underwent%20an%20emergency%20tracheotomy%20and%20was%20placed%20in%20an%20iron%20lung%20to%20help%20his%20body%20combat%20the%20deadly%20disease.%20He%20has%20relied%20on%20the%20neck-to-toe%20machine%20to%20survive%20since%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20old%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fsociety%2F2020%2Fmay%2F26%2Flast-iron-lung-paul-alexander-polio-coronavirus%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20the%20machine%20doesn't%20allow%20him%20to%20move%2C%20cough%20or%20wheeze.%20His%20field%20of%20view%20is%20also%20limited.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20his%20other%20children%20who%20underwent%20the%20same%20surgery%2C%20he%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20outlet%2C%20%26quot%3BAs%20far%20as%20you%20can%20see%2C%20rows%20and%20rows%20of%20iron%20lungs.%20Full%20of%20children.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Alexander%20said%20he%20couldn't%20make%20any%20friends%20because%20%26quot%3Bevery%20time%20I'd%20make%20a%20friend%2C%20they'd%20die%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20recalled%20doctors%20talking%20about%20him%20that%20%26quot%3Bhe's%20going%20to%20die%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3Bhe%20shouldn't%20be%20alive%26quot%3B.%20It%20made%20him%20furious.%20It%20made%20him%20want%20to%20live.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20explained%20to%20The%20Guardian%20that%20by%20the%20time%20newer%20machines%20were%20developed%2C%20he%20had%20become%20used%20to%20his%20%26quot%3Bold%20iron%20horse%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20employs%20a%20technique%20called%20%26quot%3Bfrog%20breathing%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20uses%20the%20throat%20muscles%20to%20force%20air%20past%20the%20vocal%20cords%2C%20allowing%20the%20patient%20to%20swallow%20oxygen%20one%20mouthful%20at%20a%20time%2C%20pushing%20it%20down%20the%20throat%20and%20into%20the%20lungs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20finishing%20school%2C%20Mr%20Alexander%20graduated%20with%20a%20law%20degree%20and%20practiced%20law%20for%20several%20years.%20He%20says%20his%20never%20giving%20up%20spirit%20has%20brought%20him%20this%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693553460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fov63bdd8_paul-alexander-polio-1200_625x300_01_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpolio-infected-man-has-survived-living-inside-iron-lung-for-70-years-read-his-story-4347723%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20iron%20lung%20employs%20a%20technique%20called%20%26quot%3Bfrog%20breathing%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20uses%20the%20throat%20muscles%20to%20force%20air%20past%20the%20vocal%20cords.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpolio-infected-man-has-survived-living-inside-iron-lung-for-70-years-read-his-story-4347723%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpolio-infected-man-has-survived-living-inside-iron-lung-for-70-years-read-his-story-4347723%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpolio-infected-man-has-survived-living-inside-iron-lung-for-70-years-read-his-story-4347723%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Beacon%20of%20Hope'%3A%20What%20the%20Ramon%20Magsaysay%20Award%20Citation%20for%20Oncologist%20Ravi%20Kannan%20Says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F01112851%2FUntitled-design-9.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Surgical%20oncologist%20Ravi%20Kannan%20R.%20who%20heads%20the%20Cachar%20Cancer%20Hospital%20and%20Research%20Centre%20in%20Assam%20has%20been%20named%20one%20of%20the%20recipients%20of%20the%20Ramon%20Magsaysay%20Award%20for%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20annual%20awards%2C%20named%20after%20former%20Philippine%20president%20Ramon%20Magsaysay%2C%20are%20called%20%E2%80%98Asia%E2%80%99s%20Nobel%20prize%E2%80%99%20and%20are%20considered%20very%20prestigious.%20Earlier%20recipients%20from%20India%20include%20Satyajit%20Ray%2C%20Bezwada%20Wilson%20and%20Ravish%20Kumar%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20recipients%20this%20time%20are%20Bangladeshi%20educationist%20Korvi%20Rakshand%2C%20Timorese%20environmentalist%20Eugenio%20Lemos%2C%20and%20Filipino%20peace%20negotiator%20Miriam%20Coronel%20Ferrer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20citation%20for%20the%20award%20noted%20Kannan%E2%80%99s%20incredible%20contributions%20to%20healthcare.%20It%20noted%20that%20in%20%E2%80%9Cforgotten%E2%80%9D%20places%20like%20the%20northeast%20of%20India%2C%20where%20healthcare%20is%20often%20difficult%20or%20expensive%20to%20access%2C%20cancer%20is%20all%20the%20more%20emotionally%20and%20financially%20devastating%20for%20patients%20and%20their%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssam%E2%80%99s%20first%20cancer%20hospital%20was%20not%20opened%20until%201981%2C%20and%20the%20second%2C%20the%20Cachar%20Cancer%20Hospital%20and%20Research%20Centre%20(CCHRC)%20was%20established%20in%201996.%20The%20citation%20notes%20that%20it%20was%20the%20initiative%20of%20a%20non-profit%20society%20of%20local%20citizens%2C%20funded%20by%20public%20philanthropy%20on%20land%20provided%20by%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20Kannan%20took%20over%20as%20its%20director%20in%202007%2C%20CCHRC%20grew%20into%20an%20%E2%80%9Cinnovative%2C%20widely%20admired%2C%20full-service%20cancer%20care%20facility%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20award%E2%80%99s%20citation%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20surprised%20many%20that%20Kannan%2C%20who%20previously%20headed%20the%20surgical%20oncology%20department%20in%20Adyar%20Cancer%20Institute%2C%20a%20major%20cancer%20institute%20in%20Chennai%2C%20would%20exchange%20a%20position%20in%20a%20big%20city%20for%20a%20small%20hospital%20in%20a%20remote%20part%20of%20the%20country.%20Kannan%20had%20a%20simple%20answer.%20It%20was%20where%20he%20was%20most%20needed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKannan%E2%80%99s%20leadership%20led%20to%20CCHRC%20getting%2028%20departments%20covering%20oncology%2C%20pathology%2C%20radiology%2C%20microbiology%2C%20epidemiology%2C%20tumour%20registry%20and%20palliative%20care%2C%20and%20other%20services%20and%20specialisations.%20From%20a%20staff%20of%20only%20twenty-three%2C%20the%20hospital%20now%20employs%20451%20people%2C%20the%20award%E2%80%99s%20citation%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20includes%20the%20essential%20ways%20in%20which%20Kannan%20sought%20to%20ensure%20care%20reached%20he%20poor%2C%20who%20would%20often%20have%20to%20travel%20long%20distances%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThus%2C%20the%20hospital%20introduced%20such%20pro-poor%20initiatives%20as%20free%20treatment%2C%20food%20and%20lodging%2C%20adhoc%20employment%20for%20caregivers%2C%20and%20a%20homecare%20program.%20Hospital%20team%20members%20would%20travel%20long%20distances%20to%20train%20family%20members%20in%20pain%20management%20and%20palliative%20care%2C%20as%20well%20as%20provide%20free%20medicines.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20patient%20compliance%20rates%20rose%20to%2070%25.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CCHRC%20also%20provides%20free%20or%20subsidised%20cancer%20care%20treatments%20to%20an%20average%20of%205%2C000%20new%20patients%20annually%2C%20catering%20to%20approximately%2020%2C000%20poor%20patients%20for%20treatments%20and%20follow-ups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPTI%20also%20reports%20that%20satellite%20clinics%20have%20been%20started%20in%20Karimganj%2C%20Hailakandi%2C%20and%20Dima%20Hasao%20districts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20the%20citation%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20electing%20Ravi%20Kannan%20R.%20to%20receive%20the%202023%20Ramon%20Magsaysay%20Award%2C%20the%20board%20of%20trustees%20recognizes%20his%20devotion%20to%20his%20profession%E2%80%99s%20highest%20ideals%20of%20public%20service%2C%20his%20combination%20of%20skill%2C%20commitment%2C%20and%20compassion%20in%20pushing%20the%20boundaries%20of%20people-centered%2C%20pro-poor%20health%20care%20and%20cancer%20care%2C%20and%20for%20having%20built%2C%20without%20expectation%20of%20reward%2C%20a%20beacon%20of%20hope%20for%20millions%20in%20the%20Indian%20state%20of%20Assam%2C%20thus%20setting%20a%20shining%20example%20for%20all.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693553400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F01112851%2FUntitled-design-9.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Framon-magsaysay-ravi-kannan-cachar-hospital%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kannan%20is%20a%20visionary%20medical%20professional%20and%20heads%20the%20Cachar%20Cancer%20Hospital%20and%20Research%20Centre%20in%20Assam%2C%20which%20took%20up%20enormous%20efforts%20to%20ensure%20care%20to%20the%20poor%20under%20his%20leadership.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Framon-magsaysay-ravi-kannan-cachar-hospital%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hiring%20dips%205%25%20in%20August%2C%20surge%20in%20IT%20salaries%20defies%20experience%20level%20norn%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693553346000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-05%2F10%2Ffull%2F1683702895-4936.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fhiring-dips-5-in-august-surge-in-it-salaries-defies-experience-level-norn-123090100385_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22foundit%20Insights%20Tracker%2C%20showcased%20a%205%25%20decrease%20in%20the%20proportion%20of%20employers%20hiring%20in%20August%2023%20as%20compared%20to%20the%20previous%20year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fhiring-dips-5-in-august-surge-in-it-salaries-defies-experience-level-norn-123090100385_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fhiring-dips-5-in-august-surge-in-it-salaries-defies-experience-level-norn-123090100385_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fhiring-dips-5-in-august-surge-in-it-salaries-defies-experience-level-norn-123090100385_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Review%3A%20Babil%20Khan%20Puts%20His%20Best%20Foot%20Forward%20In%20Friday%20Night%20Plan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBoys%20will%20be%20boys%2C%20boisterous%2C%20bristling%20and%20brazen%20especially%20when%20no%20one%20is%20watching%2C%20but%20the%20ones%20we%20meet%20in%20%3Cem%3EFriday%20Night%20Plan%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20teen%20comedy%20written%20and%20directed%20by%20debutant%20Vatsal%20Neelakantan%2C%20are%20a%20tame%20bunch%20by%20the%20established%20standards%20of%20the%20genre.%20They%20aren't%20reminiscent%20of%20the%20sort%20of%20guys%20who%20pushed%20the%20boundaries%20of%20exuberance%20in%20American%20Pie%20or%20Superbad.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20Mumbai%20boys%20are%20straightlaced%20kids%20in%20quest%20of%20some%20harmless%20fun%20at%20a%20turning%20point%20of%20their%20lives.%20They%20certainly%20aren't%20looking%20to%20lose%20their%20virginity.%20All%20that%20they%20intend%20to%20do%20in%20the%20course%20of%20a%20few%20hours%20of%20hard%2C%20booze-soaked%20partying%20a%20week%20ahead%20of%20their%20prom%20night%20is%20find%20girlfriends%20to%20accompany%20them%20to%20the%20ball.%20The%20worst%20that%20they%20can%20do%20while%20they%20are%20at%20it%20is%20get%20as%20sloshed%20as%20possible%20without%20passing%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFriday%20Night%20Plan%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20produced%20by%20Excel%20Entertainment%20for%20Netflix%2C%20revolves%20around%20two%20temperamentally%20dissimilar%20teenage%20brothers%20who%20bicker%2C%20banter%2C%20indulge%20in%20pillow%20fights%20and%20generally%20get%20in%20each%20other's%20ways%20in%20as%20many%20ways%20as%20they%20can.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20film%20is%20flighty%2C%20fluffy%20and%20feathery%2C%20as%20comedies%20of%20this%20kind%20usually%20are%2C%20but%20it%20is%20also%20agreeably%20diverting%20thanks%20in%20part%20to%20a%20screenplay%20that%20manages%20to%20conjure%20something%20out%20of%20literally%20nothing.%20That%20is%20not%20to%20suggest%20that%20there%20is%20anything%20magical%20in%20%3Cem%3EFriday%20Night%20Plan%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20bit%20like%20the%20boys%20it%20revolves%20around%20-%20staid%20and%20unexciting%20-%20notwithstanding%20the%20mild%20froth%20it%20whips%20up.%20It%20is%20a%20coming-of-age%20film%20that%20isn't%20wacky%20or%20wild%20enough%20to%20suck%20the%20audience%20into%20the%20whirligig%20of%20high%20school%20life%20or%20into%20the%20topsy-turvy%20inner%20worlds%20of%20on-the-cusp-of-college%20boys%20and%20girls%20determined%20to%20make%20the%20most%20of%20the%20leapfrog%20into%20adulthood.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESid%20Menon%20(Babil%20Khan)%2C%2018%2C%20is%20a%20nerdy%20young%20man%20a%20week%20or%20so%20away%20from%20graduating%20from%20high%20school.%20His%20focus%20is%20squarely%20on%20college%20applications%20but%20he%20is%20no%20hurry.%20He%20is%20wary%20of%20going%20wrong.%20It%20is%20not%20a%20day%20too%20soon%20for%20him%20to%20learn%20to%20chill%20and%20throw%20caution%20to%20the%20wind%2C%20if%20only%20occasionally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20brother%2C%20Adi%20Menon%20(Amrith%20Jayan)%2C%2016%2C%20is%20far%20more%20adventurous.%20He%20is%20forever%20up%20to%20mischief%2C%20a%20trait%20that%20Sid%20frowns%20upon.%20So%2C%20when%20Adi%20wants%20to%20go%20and%20watch%20Sid%20warm%20the%20bench%20during%20school%20football%20tournament%20final%2C%20the%20latter%20wants%20his%20ki%20brother%20off%20his%20back.%20His%20mother%20(Juhi%20Chawla%20in%20a%20special%20appearance)%20talks%20him%20out%20of%20his%20firm%20disinclination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMom%20leaves%20for%20Pune%20for%20a%20business%20meeting%20but%20not%20before%20she%20makes%20her%20older%20son%20promise%20that%20the%20brothers%20will%20stay%20out%20of%20trouble.%20But%20that%20is%20easier%20said%20than%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20sooner%20is%20their%20mother%20on%20her%20way%20than%20the%20two%20siblings%20are%20ready%20to%20firm%20up%20plans%20to%20head%20to%20a%20party%20at%20the%20home%20of%20the%20school's%20most%20popular%20girl%2C%20Natasha%20%26quot%3BNat%26quot%3B%20Sabharwal%20(Medha%20Rana)%2C%20and%20her%20little%20sister%2C%20Nitya%20%26quot%3BNits%26quot%3B%20Sabharwal%20(Aadhya%20Anand).%20On%20their%20way%20there%2C%20the%20duo%20hits%20a%20rough%20patch.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20week%20ahead%20of%20prom%20night.%20The%20boys%20and%20their%20mates%2C%20following%20the%20football%20match%20that%20throws%20up%20an%20unlikely%20star%2C%20decide%20to%20let%20their%20hair%20down%2C%20guzzle%20bucketloads%20of%20beer%20and%20play%20party%20games%20while%20utilising%20the%20evening%20looking%20around%20for%20a%20prom%20companion.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFriday%20Night%20Plan%20%3C%2Fem%3Eunpacks%20itself%20in%20four%20principal%20spaces%20-%20Sid%20and%20Adi's%20home%3B%20the%20school's%20football%20ground%20where%20Sid%20achieves%20a%20breakthrough%20that%20opens%20a%20door%20he%20did%20know%20existed%3B%20the%20streets%20of%20Mumbai%20and%20the%20venue%20of%20the%20party%20-%20before%20the%20brothers%20wind%20up%20in%20a%20police%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20all%20pans%20out%20over%20a%20single%20night%20that%20throws%20Sid%20into%20slippery%20situations.%20Adi%2C%20unflustered%2C%20has%20a%20way%20of%20treating%20every%20kerfuffle%20with%20an%20air%20of%20nonchalance%2C%20which%20annoys%20Sid%20no%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20war%20of%20pranks%20erupts%20between%20two%20groups%20of%20boys.%20It%20escalates%20rapidly%20and%20the%20two%20brothers%20find%20themselves%20in%20the%20crosshairs%20of%20a%20Mumbai%20policeman%20on%20duty%2C%20Sub-inspector%20Suhas%20Pingale%20(Ninad%20Kamat).%20As%20time%20runs%20out%20on%20them%2C%20they%20have%20a%20serious%20matter%20to%20resolve%2C%20home%20in%20on%20a%20girlfriend%20each%2C%20and%20make%20their%20way%20back%20home%20before%20their%20mother%20returns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20misadventures%20of%20the%20two%20callow%20boys%2C%20the%20film%20drops%20a%20few%20truth%20bombs%20as%20Sid%20and%20Adi%20alternate%20between%20blaming%20each%20other%20and%20sheepishly%20feeling%20fleeting%20fraternal%20fervour%20and%20even%20exchanging%20apologies.%20All%20this%20happens%20while%20the%20elder%20brother%2C%20now%20somewhat%20free%20of%20his%20inhibitions%2C%20loosens%20up%20with%20both%20Nat%20and%20Nits%2C%20the%20two%20sisters%20who%2C%20like%20the%20Menon%20boys%2C%20have%20nothing%20in%20common%20as%20far%20as%20their%20priorities%20in%20life%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFriday%20Night%20Plan%20%3C%2Fem%3Erests%20on%20a%20thin%20storyline%20that%20is%20built%20on%20the%20clash%20of%20the%20character%20contrasts%20that%20separate%20and%20define%20the%20four%20key%20individuals%20in%20the%20story.%20Nat%20is%20the%20gregarious%20one.%20Nits%20is%20an%20introvert%2C%20a%20bookworm%20who%20is%20at%20her%20best%20when%20she%20is%20lost%20in%20her%20thoughts.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESid%20has%20to%20contend%20with%20a%20formidable%20rival%20in%20Kabir%20(Aditya%20Jain)%2C%20the%20star%20footballer%20of%20the%20school%2C%20in%20his%20attempts%20to%20earn%20Nat's%20attention.%20As%20the%20night%20wears%20on%2C%20the%20pints%20he%20downs%20help%20Sid%20step%20out%20of%20his%20shell%20much%20to%20the%20delight%20of%20his%20kid%20brother.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInsubstantial%20as%20it%20might%20be%20as%20a%20coming-of-age%20drama%2C%20Friday%20Night%20Plan%20works%20in%20parts%20because%20the%20two%20male%20leads%20get%20into%20the%20swing%20of%20things%20without%20much%20ado.%20Babil%20Khan%20puts%20his%20best%20foot%20forward%20as%20the%20honest-to-goodness%20guy%20who%20is%20overly%20circumspect%2C%20a%20boy%20who%20prefers%20to%20keep%20to%20himself%20until%20a%20couple%20of%20incidents%20catapult%20him%20into%20the%20spotlight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmrith%20Jayan%20as%20the%20chirpy%20younger%20brother%20who%20revels%20in%20pushing%20his%20luck%20is%20no%20less%20impressive.%20In%20the%20role%20of%20the%20boys'%20mother%2C%20Juhi%20Chawla%20is%20effortlessly%20in%20step%20with%20the%20flow%20of%20the%20not-too-demanding%20film.%20Ninad%20Kamat%20as%20the%20angry%20cop%20lying%20in%20wait%20to%20read%20the%20brothers%20the%20riot%20act%20has%20his%20moments%20under%20the%20sun%2C%20er%20moon.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20others%20in%20the%20cast%20keep%20the%20flimsy%20but%20inoffensive%20romp%20moving%20along%20with%20their%20zestful%20performances.%20Both%20Medha%20Rana%20and%20Aadhya%20Anand%20do%20their%20very%20best%20in%20a%20film%20that%20is%20not%20so%20much%20about%20what%20the%20girls%20want%20as%20about%20two%20boys%20compelled%20to%20grow%20up%20in%20the%20matter%20of%20a%20few%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFriday%20Night%20Plan%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Emay%20not%20be%20the%20most%20happening%20cinematic%20party%20you%20will%20ever%20be%20invited%20to%2C%20but%20it%20is%20the%20sort%20of%20modest-scale%2C%20light-hearted%20entertainer%20that%20does%20not%20lose%20the%20spring%20in%20its%20dainty%20steps%20although%20it%20never%20quite%20turns%20into%20a%20full-fledged%20foxtrot.%2