2F103273894.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%E2%80%99s%20Crude%20Oil%20Imports%20from%20Russia%20Down%20by%2020%25%2C%20Saudi%20Oil%20is%20Back%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F28110029%2F11147221423_303ec1a1d8_c.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20India%E2%80%99s%20crude%20oil%20import%20in%20August%20has%20come%20down%20drastically.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20has%20fallen%20by%2020%25%20last%20month%2C%20down%20from%20120%20thousand%20per%20barrel%20a%20day%20(kbd)%20to%204.45%20million%20a%20barrel%20per%20day%20(mbd).%20This%20is%20due%20to%20a%20reduction%20in%20its%20controversial%20and%20much%20discussed%20oil%20import%20from%20Russia.%20The%20figures%20were%20put%20out%20by%20Vortexa%2C%20a%20London-based%20market%20intelligence%20provider.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20had%20imported%202.1%20mbd%20from%20Russia%20in%20July%202023%2C%20but%20in%20August%2C%20it%20fell%20to%20the%20lowest%20amount%20in%20seven%20months%2C%20to%201.63%20mbd.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIndia%E2%80%99s%20crude%20imports%20in%20July%20reached%20a%20three-month%20high%20of%204.58%20mbd.%20Strong%20domestic%20and%20exported%20crude%20oil%20demand%20had%20buoyed%20refiners%20to%20operate%20at%20high%20utilisation%20that%20month.%20In%20August%202023%2C%20lower%20crude%20imports%20from%20Russia%20saw%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20total%20imports%20retreat.%20At%20least%20two%20refineries%20have%20shut%20down%20for%20planned%20maintenance%2C%20and%20several%20more%20are%20scheduled%20over%20this%20quarter%20and%20next%2C%E2%80%9D%20Serena%20Huang%2C%20an%20analyst%20at%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fbusiness%2F2023%2Fsep%2F01%2Fcrude-oil-imports-from-russia-fell-20-in-august-2610629.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EVortexa%20is%20cited%20as%20saying%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20New%20Indian%20Express.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETraditional%20suppliers%20to%20India%20of%20crude%20oil%2C%20West%20Asia%20mainly%2C%20appear%20to%20be%20back%20in%20business.%20Saudi%20Arabia%20has%20re-emerged%20as%20a%20key%20supplier%20of%20crude%20oil%20to%20India.%20India%E2%80%99s%20crude%20imports%20from%20Saudi%20Arabia%20rebounded%20by%2060%25%20month-on-month%20to%20840%20kbd%20in%20August.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98A%20depleting%20account%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20believed%20that%20the%20reason%20for%20the%20drop%20in%20imports%20from%20Russia%20is%20%E2%80%9Ca%20depleting%20discount.%E2%80%9D%20The%20discount%20on%20Russian%20oil%20is%20said%20to%20have%20fallen%20drastically%20from%20%2415%20a%20barrel%20to%20%245%20a%20barrel.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIndia%E2%80%99s%20imports%20of%20Russian%20crude%20were%20down%20440%20kbd%20in%20August%20to%201.63%20mbd%2C%20and%20discounts%20on%20Russian%20Urals%20against%20dated%20Brent%20have%20narrowed%20on%20a%20FOB%20basis.%20Given%20higher%20dated%20Brent%20prices%20in%20recent%20weeks%2C%20this%20means%20that%20Russian%20Urals%20is%20now%20likely%20more%20expensive%20when%20sold%20on%20a%20DES%20basis%20to%20Indian%20refiners%2C%E2%80%9D%20Serene%20Huang%2C%20analyst%20at%20Vortexa%20is%20quoted%20as%20saying.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERecently%2C%20Russia%20announced%20voluntary%20output%20cuts%20of%20500%2C000%20barrels%20a%20day%20in%20August%20and%20300%2C000%20barrels%20a%20day%20in%20September%2C%20mainly%20of%20Urals%20grade%2C%20according%20to%20Russian%20officials.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERussia%20overcame%20EU%20ban%20due%20to%20Indian%20imports%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndian%20imports%20of%20Russian%20crude%20have%20made%20global%20news%2C%20as%20they%20helped%20Russia%20ride%20out%20the%20difficulties%20that%20the%20EU%20ban%20on%20Russian%20oil%20imposed%20in%20December%202022%20posed%20for%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EData%20on%20the%20discharge%20volume%20by%20destination%20ports%20in%20India%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vortexa.com%2Finsights%2Farticle%2Frussia-overcomes-eu-ban-with-record-high-crude-exports-to-india%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eaccording%20to%20Vortexa%20in%20January%20this%20year%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20revealed%20that%20private%20refiners%20have%20led%20the%20increase%20in%20Russian%20crude%20purchases.%20Their%20%E2%80%9Cshare%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20crude%20imports%20from%20Russia%20increased%20from%2040%25%20during%20July-November%20last%20year%2C%20to%2048%25%20in%20December%2C%20rising%20further%20to%2060%25%20in%20January.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2Finteractive%2F2023%2F06%2F22%2Fbusiness%2Findia-russia-oil.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20June%20on%20the%20role%20of%20so-called%20certain%20%E2%80%98laundromat%E2%80%99%20countries%2C%20%E2%80%9Cchief%20among%20whom%20was%20India%2C%20as%20well%20as%20China%2C%20Turkey%2C%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20and%20Singapore.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20cited%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fenergyandcleanair.org%2Fpublication%2Fthe-laundromat-how-the-price-cap-coalition-whitewashes-russian-oil-in-third-countries%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereport%20in%20April%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20put%20out%20by%20the%20Centre%20for%20Research%20on%20Energy%20and%20Clean%20Air%2C%20a%20research%20group%20based%20in%20Finland.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20%E2%80%98laundromat%E2%80%99%20countries%20were%20ones%20that%20bought%20Russian%20oil%2C%20refined%20it%20into%20other%20products%20and%20sell%20it%20on%20to%20buyers%20in%20Europe%2C%20the%20United%20States%20and%20other%20jurisdictions%20that%20have%20halted%20direct%20purchases%20from%20Russia.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EControversies%20in%20India%20over%20Russian%20Oil%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOther%20than%20the%20role%20of%20private%20refiners%20cornering%20benefits%20of%20Russian%20oil%20imports%2C%20there%20was%20controversy%20over%20other%20aspects%20of%20Russian%20oil%20imports%20in%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20purported%20use%20of%20the%20Chinese%20Yuan%20to%20foot%20the%20bill%20for%20it%20to%20dodge%20the%20sanctions%20raised%20eyebrows.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Findia%2Findia-cenbank-give-banks-guidance-resolve-rupee-trade-issues-official-2023-07-14%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EQuoting%20a%20senior%20government%20official%2C%20Reuters%20reported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20%E2%80%9CIndian%20refiners%20have%20settled%20some%20payments%20for%20Russian%20oil%20imports%20in%20Chinese%20yuan%2C%E2%80%9D%20even%20as%20the%20US%20dollar%20remains%20the%20dominant%20currency%20for%20such%20payments.%20There%20was%20no%20official%20denial%20of%20this%20report.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThen%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F6f81585c-321a-41fb-bcdb-579e93381671%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EFinancial%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3ETimes%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Findia-russia-oil-trade-gatik-ship-management%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Cmysterious%20Mumbai%20company%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20registered%20as%20an%20exporter%20on%20March%2031%202023%2C%20which%20has%20grown%20into%20a%20giant%20of%20inter