%20are%20at%20a%20very%20crucial%20stage%20now.%20Both%20the%20central%20and%20the%20state%20governments%20are%20confused%20about%20whom%20to%20talk%20to.%20We%20will%20go%20with%20the%20public%20(opinion)%20and%20never%20work%20against%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20news%20agency%20PTI%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fnorth-east%2Ftoo-many-civil-bodies-in-manipur-they-need-to-talk-in-single-voice-cm-biren-singh%2Fcid%2F1962889%5C%22%3Equoted%3C%2Fa%3E%20Singh%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20appealed%20to%20civic%20bodies%20to%20come%20up%20with%20a%20concrete%20proposal%20and%20to%20speak%20in%20one%20voice%20so%20that%20it%20could%20be%20conveyed%20to%20the%20Union%20government%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20violence%20continuing%20unabated%20for%20months%20now%2C%20even%20civil%20society%20organisations%20are%20divided%20on%20community%20lines.%20Both%20Meiteis%20and%20Kukis%2C%20the%20warring%20factions%2C%20have%20community%20organisations%20of%20their%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Kukis%20are%20represented%20by%20organisations%20such%20as%20the%20Indigenous%20Tribal%20Leaders%20Forum%20(ITLF)%2C%20Committee%20On%20Tribal%20Unity%20(COTU)%2C%20Kuki%20Inpi%20and%20the%20Zomi%20Council%2C%20Meiteis%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20have%20their%20own%20bodies%20such%20as%20the%20Coordinating%20Committee%20on%20Manipur%20Integrity%20(COCOMI)%2C%20United%20Committee%20Manipur%20(UCM)%2C%20and%20the%20All%20Manipur%20United%20Clubs%20Organisation%20(AMUCO).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20minister%20made%20his%20comments%20at%20the%20state-level%20celebration%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98Meri%20Maati%20Mera%20Desh%E2%80%99%20programme%20on%20Thursday.%20It%20aims%20for%20a%20unified%20celebration%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20soil%20and%20valour%2C%20commemorating%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20journey%20of%20freedom%20and%20progress.%20This%20campaign%20comprises%20many%20activities%20and%20ceremonies%20conducted%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20and%20civil%20society%20organisations%20should%20come%20together%20and%20take%20a%20concrete%20proposal%20showing%20their%20stand%20so%20that%20the%20government%20can%20convey%20it%20to%20the%20Centre.%20We%20must%20come%20together%20irrespective%20of%20our%20political%20and%20community%20affiliation%20and%20work%20together%20for%20the%20present%20and%20future%20generation%20to%20enable%20them%20to%20live%20with%20dignity%2C%E2%80%9D%20Singh%20said%20at%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20condemned%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmanipur-two-more-killed-firing-churachandpur-bishnupur-border%5C%22%3Egun%20attacks%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20August%2029%2C%20on%20farmers%20tending%20their%20fields%20at%20Naransena%20in%20Bishnupur%20district.%20%E2%80%9CSecurity%20forces%20arrested%20one%20person%20in%20this%20connection%20along%20with%20a%20.303%20rifle%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Singh%20may%20have%20been%20appealing%20for%20peace%2C%20there%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmanipur-tribal-mlas-refute-biren-singhs-claim-say-not-in-touch-with-cm%5C%22%3Eallegations%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20him%20that%20he%20has%20been%20favouring%20Meiteis%20in%20the%20ongoing%20conflict%2C%20given%20that%20he%20is%20a%20Meitei%20himself.%20Legislators%20from%20his%20own%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20belonging%20to%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20community%20have%20urged%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20remove%20him%20to%20find%20a%20solution%20to%20the%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20May%203%2C%20when%20the%20violence%20first%20broke%20out%2C%20more%20than%20160%20people%20have%20lost%20their%20lives%20and%20several%20thousands%20have%20been%20displaced%20from%20their%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693551612000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fup