273689.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BFirst%20And%20Last%20Time%26quot%3B%3A%20SRK%20On%20His%20Bald%20Look%20In%20Jawan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EShah%20Rukh%20Khan%20showcased%20the%20trailer%20of%20%3Ci%3EJawan%3C%2Fi%3E%20at%20the%20iconic%20Burj%20Khalifa%20building%20in%20Dubai%20where%20he%20spoke%20about%20the%20universal%20appeal%20of%20cinema%20and%20how%20his%20fans%20will%20see%20him%20in%20a%20bald%20avatar%20for%20the%20first%20and%20the%20last%20time.The%20actor%2C%20who%20has%20a%20massive%20fan%20following%20in%20the%20UAE%2C%20has%20been%20on%20a%20promotional%20spree%20ahead%20of%20the%20film's%20release%20on%20September%207%20in%20Hindi%2C%20Tamil%20and%20Telugu.%20Shah%20Rukh%20performed%20with%20a%20dance%20troupe%20on%20the%20song%20%3Ci%3EZinda%20Banda%3C%2Fi%3E%20from%20the%20film%20at%20the%20event%2C%20also%20attended%20by%20director%20Atlee%20and%20music%20composer%20Anirudh%20Ravichander.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actor%20said%20the%20film%20will%20offer%20something%20unique%20to%20all%20the%20people%20and%20he%20will%20be%20seen%20in%20%26quot%3B6%20to%207%20getups%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BI'm%20even%20bald%20in%20the%20film%2C%20so%20that's%20something%20I'm%20never%20ever%20going%20to%20be%20in%20my%20life.%20It%20was%20the%20first%20and%20the%20last%20time.%3Ci%3E%20Abhi%20aap%20logo%20ke%20liye%20main%20ganja%20bhi%20ho%20gaya%20hu.%20To%20issi%20ki%20izzat%20ke%20liye%20chale%20jaana...%20Mujhe%20ganja%20hone%20ka%20ya%20dekhne%20ka%20mauka%20mile%20ya%20na%20mile%2C%20kya%20pata%3C%2Fi%3E%20(I%20even%20went%20bald%20for%20you%20all.%20At%20least%2C%20honour%20that%20and%20watch%20the%20film%20in%20theatres.%20You%20may%20or%20may%20not%20get%20another%20chance%20to%20see%20me%20bald).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%202%20hour%20and%2045%20minute%20film%2C%20I%20hope%20you%20enjoy%20all%20that%20we%20have%20dealt%20with%20in%20the%20film%2C%26quot%3B%20Shah%20Rukh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20film's%20trailer%20was%20projected%20on%20the%20iconic%20building%20during%20the%20event%2C%20where%20Shah%20Rukh%20and%20the%20team%20also%20launched%20the%20Arabic%20version%20of%20the%20movie's%20popular%20song%20%3Ci%3EChaleya%3C%2Fi%3E.%20The%20promotional%20event%20was%20attended%20by%20over%2020%2C000%20people%2C%20according%20to%20the%20makers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EJawan%3C%2Fi%3E%20is%20very%20special%20for%20us%20because%20somewhere%20we%20realised%20that%20entertainment%2C%20what%20we%20entertain%20you%20with%2C%20it%20should%20have%20no%20language%2C%20religion%2C%20caste%2C%20colour%2C%20creed%20or%20any%20kind%20of%20distinction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20should%20all%20come%20together%20to%20celebrate%20entertainment%20with%20our%20families%2C%20loved%20ones.%20This%20is%20the%20first%20step%20in%20that%20direction.%20So%20we%20made%20the%20film%20in%20Tamil%20and%20Telugu%2C%20and%20tonight%2C%20the%20attempt%20is%20also%20to%20release%20a%20song%20in%20Arabic%2C%26quot%3B%20the%2057-year-old%20actor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EJawan%3C%2Fi%3E%20is%20billed%20as%20a%20high-octane%20action%20thriller%20that%20outlines%20the%20emotional%20journey%20of%20a%20man%20who%20is%20set%20to%20rectify%20the%20wrongs%20in%20the%20society%2C%20according%20to%20the%20official%20synopsis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EJawan%3C%2Fi%3E%20is%20about%20people%20who%20may%20not%20be%20as%20good%2C%20well-off%20as%20you%20and%20I%20are%2C%20and%20we%20need%20to%20have%20justice%20for%20them.%20We%20need%20to%20empower%20the%20biggest%20force%20in%20the%20world%2C%20which%20is%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20this%20film%20is%20all%20about%20that%20but%20there%20is%20lot%20of%20love%2C%20happiness%2C%20action%2C%20emotion%20and%20drama%2C%20all%20of%20it%20will%20be%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20Shah%20Rukh%20said%20at%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20film%20also%20features%20Nayanthara%20and%20Vijay%20Sethupathi%20as%20well%20as%20Deepika%20Padukone%20in%20a%20special%20appearance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actor%20said%20%3Ci%3EJawan%3C%2Fi%3E%20has%20a%20lot%20of%20%26quot%3Brelationship%2C%20outstanding%20action%20and%20great%20background%20music%26quot%3B%20by%20Ravichander.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20praised%20Atlee%2C%20known%20for%20delivering%20hits%20like%20%3Ci%3ETheri%2C%20Mersal%3C%2Fi%3E%20and%20%3Ci%3EBigil%3C%2Fi%3E%20with%20superstar%20Thalapathy%20Vijay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20director%20who%20have%20made%20some%20of%20the%20biggest%20mass%20films...%20He%20is%20a%20monster%20and%20gangster%20of%20a%20filmmaker%2C%20and%20this%20is%20his%20first%20foray%20into%20Hindi%20cinema%2C%20him%20and%20his%20wife%20Priya.%20They%20have%20worked%20really%20hard.%20The%20whole%20team%20has%20worked%20very%20hard%2C%26quot%3B%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EActors%20Sanya%20Malhotra%2C%20Priyamani%2C%20Girija%20Oak%2C%20Sanjeeta%20Bhattacharya%2C%20Lehar%20Khan%2C%20Aaliyah%20Qureshi%2C%20Ridhi%20Dogra%2C%20Sunil%20Grover%20and%20Mukesh%20Chhabra%20also%20appear%20in%20the%20movie%20in%20key%20roles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Red%20Chillies%20Entertainment%20presentation%2C%20%3Ci%3EJawan%3C%2Fi%3E%20is%20produced%20by%20Gauri%20Khan%20and%20co-produced%20by%20Gaurav%20Verma.%20It%20will%20hit%20the%20theatres%20on%20September%207%20in%20Hindi%2C%20Tamil%20and%20Telugu%20languages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693551240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fjb1m0p8o_srk_625x300_01_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fi-went-bald-for-a-film-for-first-and-last-time-says-shah-rukh-khan-at-jawan-dubai-event-4347534%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20actor%20said