20journey%20by%20himself.%20Besides%20Moneeka%2C%20whose%20companionship%20and%20assistance%20was%20a%20crucial%20source%20of%20strength%20for%20him%2C%20a%20long%20line%20of%20superb%20Chhattisgarhi%20performers%20were%20equal%20partners%20in%20the%20journey%2C%20lending%20it%20a%20brilliance%20rarely%20seen%20on%20Indian%20stage.%20Thakurdas%2C%20Madan%20Lal%2C%20Lalu%20Ram%2C%20Bhulwa%20Yadave%2C%20Brij%20Lal%2C%20Udayram%20Srivas%2C%20Devi%20Lal%20Nag%2C%20Fida%20Bai%2C%20Mala%20Bai%2C%20Ramcharan%20Nirmalkar%2C%20Ravi%20Lal%2C%20Agesh%20Nag%2C%20Govind%20Lal%20Nirmalkar%2C%20Deepak%20Tiwari%2C%20Poonam%20Tiwari%2C%20Chait%20Ram%20Yadav%20%E2%80%93%20what%20a%20vibrant%20galaxy%20of%20stage%20actors!%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESadly%2C%20except%20for%20a%20few%20(Ravi%2C%20Agesh%2C%20and%20Poonam)%20no%20other%20artiste%20from%20this%20group%20of%20memorable%20artistes%20survives%20today.%20But%20those%20of%20us%20who%20saw%20them%20on%20stage%20still%20have%20their%20faces%20and%20the%20mesmerising%20power%20of%20their%20acting%20vividly%20etched%20in%20our%20memory.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20this%20partnership%20that%20lay%20behind%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ethose%20memorable%20masterpieces%E2%80%94%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAgra%20Bazaar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMitti%20ki%20Gadi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ECharandas%20Chor%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBahadur%20Kalarin%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ELala%20Shohrat%20Rai%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EShajapur%20ki%20Shantibai%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHirma%20ki%20Amar%20Kahani%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EKamdeo%20ka%20Apna%20Basant%20Ritu%20ka%20Sapna%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%