l%20sector.%20While%20some%20of%20these%20changes%20will%20come%20into%20effect%20on%20the%20first%20day%2C%20others%20later%20in%20the%20month.%20We%20have%20listed%20some%20of%20the%20big%20ones%2C%20which%20can%20have%20a%20huge%20impact%20on%20people's%20finance.%20These%20changes%20are%20also%20connected%20to%20Aadhaar%20update%20and%20linking%20of%20the%20identity%20document%20with%20the%20PAN%20card.%20Those%20holding%20Axis%20Bank's%20credit%20cards%20will%20also%20be%20impacted%20by%20the%20changes%20coming%20into%20effect%20from%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsers%20of%20Axis%20Bank's%20Magnus%20credit%20card%20will%20have%20to%20pay%20more%20from%20today.%20The%20bank%20has%20mentioned%20about%20the%20changes%20in%20terms%20and%20conditions.%20The%20biggest%20change%20is%20the%20revision%20in%20annual%20fee%2C%20which%20has%20been%20revised%20from%20Rs%2010%2C000%20(plus%20GST)%20to%20Rs%2012%2C500%20(plus%20GST).%20The%20benefits%20being%20given%20along%20with%20the%20card%20have%20also%20been%20revised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deadline%20to%20update%20details%20in%20the%20Aadhaar%20card%20for%20free%20will%20end%20this%20month.%20The%20Unique%20Identification%20Authority%20of%20India%20(UIDAI)%20had%20extended%20the%20last%20date%20from%20June%2014%20to%20September%2014%2C%202023.%20The%20scheme%20was%20launched%20for%20those%20citizens%20who%20had%20got%20their%20Aadhaar%20issued%2010%20years%20ago%20and%20have%20not%20updated%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20month%20will%20also%20give%20last%20chance%20to%20people%20to%20exchange%20Rs%202%2C000%20notes.%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20(RBI)%20had%20said%20in%20May%20that%20people%20can%20exchange%20or%20deposit%20them%20in%20their%20bank%20accounts%20by%20the%20said%20date.%20The%20central%20bank%20said%20people%20can%20deposit%20or%20exchange%20for%20lower%20denomination%20notes%20till%20September%2030%20for%20up%20to%20Rs%2020%2C000%20at%20a%20time.%20However%2C%20a%20source%20told%20NDTV%20that%20even%20if%20anyone%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frs-2-000-notes-to-be-withdrawn-from-circulation-exchange-them-by-september-30-2023-says-rbi-4049268%5C%22%3ERs%202%2C000%20notes%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20the%20current%20deadline%2C%20it%20will%20remain%20a%20valid%20tender.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20current%20financial%20year%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Finance%20made%20the%20Permanent%20Account%20Number%20(PAN)%20and%20Aadhaar%20card%20mandatory%20for%20making%20investments%20in%20small%20saving%20schemes%20like%20Public%20Provident%20Fund%20(PPF)%2C%20Post%20Office%20Saving%20Scheme%20and%20Senior%20Citizens%20Saving%20Scheme%20(SCSS).%20For%20existing%20subscribers%2C%20Aadhaar%20number%20will%20have%20to%20be%20submitted%20by%20September%2030%2C%20failing%20which%20their%20accounts%20will%20be%20frozen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20deadline%20that%20people%20need%20to%20keep%20in%20mind%20is%20the%20nomination%20facility%20for%20trading%20and%20demat%20accounts.%20The%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%20(SEBI)%20had%2C%20in%20March%20this%20year%2C%20extended%20the%20time%20for%20holders%20of%20theses%20holders%20to%20make%20nominations%20or%20opt%20out%20of%20it.%20The%20revised%20deadline%20is%20September%2030th.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693550580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-02%2Fhd824m9o_money-generic-rupees-generic_625x300_25_February_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F5-financial-changes-coming-into-effect-from-september-read-details-4347553%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20changes%20are%20also%20connected%20to%20linking%20of%20Aadhaar%20and%20PAN%20card%20and%20exchange%20of%20Rs%202%2C000%20notes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F5-financial-changes-coming-into-effect-from-september-read-details-4347553%22%2C%