0upper%20caste%20elites%2C%20had%20in%20this%20country%20similarly%20%E2%80%9Cconstructed%E2%80%9D%20in%20venerated%20cultural-theological%20texts%20congenial%20views%20of%20the%20downtrodden%20castes%20and%20tribal%20communities%20%E2%80%93%20indeed%20of%20other%20social%20segments%20of%20the%20populace%20as%20well%2C%20including%20religious%20minorities%20%E2%80%93%20and%20used%20those%20constructions%20to%20keep%20in%20place%20the%20propertied%20hegemony%20of%20minority%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20constructions%20had%20for%20centuries%20deemed%20the%20vast%20majority%2C%20women%20included%2C%20as%20unsuited%20for%20intellectual%20pursuits%2C%20and%20thus%20useful%20only%20in%20subordinate%20situations%20to%20aid%20the%20glory%20of%20the%20land%2C%20which%20resided%20chiefly%20in%20the%20attainments%20of%20the%20twice-born.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlas%2C%20in%20the%20frenzy%20set%20in%20motion%20by%20Said%E2%80%99s%20book%2C%20only%20a%20laggard%20handful%20seemed%20to%20find%20these%20ruminations%20worthy%20of%20foregrounding%20by%20linking%20our%20own%20explorations%20to%20Said%E2%80%99s%20theoretical%20contribution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20am%20of%20course%20here%20referring%20primarily%20to%20scholarship%20from%20within%20the%20literary%20studies%20fraternity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20as%20we%20write%2C%20news%20comes%20that%20a%20Gladstone%20scion%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fuk-wales-66558156%5C%22%3Eproclaimed%3C%2Fa%3E%20their%20resolve%20to%20apologise%20for%20slavery%2C%20and%2C%20presumably%2C%20for%20the%20riches%20made%20off%20slave%20labour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20Western%20capitalism%20had%20its%20first%20roots%20in%20the%20expropriation%20of%20slave%20labour%20is%20of%20course%20by%20now%20an%20established%20fact%20of%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20to%20remind%20ourselves%2C%20there%20are%20other%20(not%20just%20the%20Gladstone%20clan)%2C%20very%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.virginiamemory.com%2Fonline-exhibitions%2Fexhibits%2Fshow%2Fto-be-sold%2Fwho-profited-%5C%22%3Edistinguished%20families%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20England%2C%20America%20and%20Europe%20whose%20pelf%20owes%20massively%20to%20the%20trans-Atlantic%20slave%20trade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Frace-oppression-colonial-slave-trade%5C%22%3Ehallowed%20academic%20institutions%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20Oxford%20and%20Yale%2C%20and%20prized%20scholarships%20to%20their%20halls%20and%20classrooms%20likewise%20owe%20their%20grandeur%20to%20moneys%20made%20by%20%E2%80%9Cgentlemen%E2%80%9D%20like%20Mr.%20Rhodes%20and%20Mr.%20Yale%20from%20the%20very%20same%20trade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClearly%2C%20Mr%20Gladsone%E2%80%99s%20conscientious%20lead%20is%20admirable%2C%20one%20that%20many%20others%20could%20emulate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EInternalising%20the%20lesson%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20again%2C%20the%20point%20remains%3A%20Are%20we%20in%20the%20erstwhile%20colonies%20who%20are%20gratified%20by%20such%20gestures%20willing%20to%20internalise%20a%20lesson%20from%20such%20historic%20initiatives%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAre%20we%20willing%20likewise%20to%20apologise%20to%20our%20Bahujan%20Indians%20(set%20down%20in%20Brahminical%20texts%20as%20Shudras%20and%20Untouchables%20and%20rated%20below%20some%20choice%20animals%20in%20significance)%20for%20the%20atrocities%20vented%20on%20them%20over%20unconscionable%20millennia%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20it%20be%20argued%20that%20modern%20India%20has%2C%20after%20all%2C%20constitutionally%20outlawed%20untouchability%2C%20so%20has%20the%20Western%20world%20abolished%20slavery%20and%20racial%20discrimination%20in%20the%20books.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20some%20there%20are%20coming%20forward%20to%20apologise%2C%20perhaps%20in%20the%20hope%20that%20such%20an%20initiative%20might%20aid%20those%20who%20fight%20the%20continuance%20in%20practice%20of%20racial%20discrimination%20in%20the%20West.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20who%20says%20untouchability%20has%20in%20practice%20ended%20in%20India%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThink%20of%20the%20honourable%20judge%20who%20had%20the%20entire%20court%20premises%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fdalit-judge-moves-sc-over-courtroom-purification%2Farticleshow%2F1637926210.cms%5C%22%3Epurified%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20with%20waters%20from%20the%20holy%20Ganges%20because%20his%20predecessor%20had%20been%20a%20Dalit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20that%20is%20about%20an%20officer%20of%20a%20court%2C%20we%20may%20well%20imagine%20what%20transpires%20among%20local%20communities%3B%20indeed%2C%20sections%20of%20the%20so-nationalist%20media%20still%2C%20thankfully%2C%20make%20bold%20to%20report%20occurrences%20of%20that%20sort.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAre%20we%20willing%20to%20apologise%20to%20legions%20of%20our%20widowed%20women%20for%20the%20unconscionable%20collective%20crime%20of%20having%20sat%20them%20on%20burning%20pyres%20on%20the%20authority%20of%20fake%20and%20mischievous%20knowledge%20so%20that%20their%20claim%20to%20family%20property%20could%20be%20erased%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAre%20we%20willing%20to%20apologise%20to%20a%20wide%20segment%20of%20our%20minorities%20for%20constantly%20%E2%80%9Cothering%E2%80%9D%20them%20so%20that%20they%20are%20%E2%80%9Cconstructed%E2%80%9D%20as%20inauthentic%20nationals%20undeserving%20of%20full%20and%20non-discriminatory%20citizenship%20rights%2C%20and%20of%20full%20and%20perceived%20equality%20before%20the%20law%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAre%20we%20willing%20to%20apologise%20to%20millions%20of%20our%20children%20who%20remain%20doomed%20to%20labour%20over%20interminable%20hours%20in%20shops%2C%20dhabas%2C%20dinghies%20and%20airless%20factories%20in%20sidelanes%20in%20town%20after%20town%2C%20even%20as%20the%20constitution%20outlaws%20such%20labour%2C%20robbing%20them%20of%20their%20fundamental%20right%20to%20education%20and%20health%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAr