was%20poor%20and%20from%20a%20lower%20caste%20and%20had%20questioned%20one%20of%20the%20teachers%20when%20she%20was%20given%20a%20fee%20receipt%20for%20an%20amount%20lower%20than%20she%20had%20actually%20paid.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20has%20come%20to%20light%20days%20after%20a%20teacher%20in%20the%20state's%20Muzaffarnagar%20had%20asked%20students%20to%20take%20turns%20slapping%20one%20of%20their%20classmates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAyesha%20Bano%20(name%20changed)%20was%20a%20student%20of%20Azimuddin%20Ashraf%20Islamia%20Inter%20College%20in%20Barabanki%20district.%20Her%20mother%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BMy%20husband%20died%20of%20a%20heart%20attack%20in%202018%20and%20our%20family%20was%20then%20on%20the%20brink%20of%20starvation.%20With%20great%20difficulty%2C%20I%20managed%20to%20admit%20Ayesha%20and%20her%20younger%20sister%20to%20the%20school%20in%202022.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20May%2027%2C%20Ayesha%20paid%20her%20school%20fees%20of%20Rs%201%2C100%20but%20one%20of%20her%20teachers%2C%20Wasfi%20Khatoon%2C%20%C2%A0gave%20her%20a%20receipt%20for%20a%20lower%20amount.%20When%20Ayesha%20pointed%20this%20out%20and%20opposed%20it%2C%20the%20teacher%20allegedly%20told%20her%20that%20despite%20being%20poor%20and%20from%20a%20lower%20caste%2C%20she%20was%20behaving%20like%20she%20was%20equal%20to%20the%20upper%20castes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20said%20Wasfi%20and%20a%20male%20teacher%20then%20made%20it%20a%20point%20to%20taunt%20Ayesha%20over%20her%20family's%20poverty%20and%20caste%20regularly%20in%20front%20of%20other%20students.%20Fed%20up%20with%20the%20constant%20harassment%2C%20Ayesha%20hanged%20herself%20at%20her%20home%20on%20August%204.%20A%20suicide%20note%20written%20by%20her%20said%20she%20was%20taking%20the%20step%20because%20of%20the%20repeated%20taunts%20by%20Wasfi%20and%20the%20other%20teacher.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20approached%20the%20police%20again%20and%20again%20for%20four%20to%20five%20days%20but%20t