0entrepreneur%20with%20no%20prior%20political%20experience%2C%20has%20seen%20his%20campaign%20gain%20momentum%2C%20leading%20to%20increased%20criticism%20from%20opponents%20such%20as%20Mike%20Pence%20and%20Nikki%20Haley.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fvivek-ramaswamy-hits-out-at-critics-says-knives-are-out-because-he-is-surging-ahead-in-presidential-race%2Farticleshow%2F103270192.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fvivek-ramaswamy-hits-out-at-critics-says-knives-are-out-because-he-is-surging-ahead-in-presidential-race%2Famp_articleshow%2F103270192.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fvivek-ramaswamy-hits-out-at-critics-says-knives-are-out-because-he-is-surging-ahead-in-presidential-race%2Famp_articleshow%2F103270192.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Now%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20%26quot%3BOutSoros-es%26quot%3B%20His%20Attack%20On%20Narendra%20Modi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20August%2031%2C%20while%2063%20leaders%20of%2028%20parties%20who%20constitute%20the%20organisation%20with%20the%20moniker%20%26quot%3BIndian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance%26quot%3B%20(INDIA)%20prepared%20for%20their%20two-day%20meet%20in%20India's%20financial%20capital%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20the%20principal%20face%20of%20its%20largest%20constituent%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20enacted%20a%20soliloquy%20that%20went%20against%20the%20very%20spirit%20of%20the%20word%20%26quot%3Balliance%26quot%3B.%20It%20belittled%20the%20word%20%26quot%3Binclusive%26quot%3B%20(as%20the%20other%2027%20parties%20were%20not%20involved%20in%20their%20media%20outreach).%20It%20belied%20the%20words%20%26quot%3Bdevelopmental%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bnational%26quot%3B%20(it%20has%20the%20potential%20of%20crashing%20India's%20stock%20market%2C%20causing%20common%20investors%20to%20lose%20money%3B%20and%20stymie%20foreign%20investment%2C%20damaging%20national%20interest).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20when%20the%20conclave%20participants%20savoured%20a%20gala%20dinner%20hosted%20by%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20chief%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%2C%20none%20of%20the%20other%20parties%20had%20endorsed%20the%20Congress%20agenda%20of%20baiting%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20the%20allegation%20of%20promoting%20crony%20capitalism%20to%20benefit%20the%20Adani%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20repeated%20his%20demand%20for%20a%20Joint%20Parliamentary%20Committee%20(JPC).%20During%20the%20past%20sessions%20of%20parliament%2C%20this%20demand%20found%20no%20takers%20among%20opposition%20parties.%20The%20Grand%20Old%20Man%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BINDIA%26quot%3B%20conglomerate%2C%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20even%20came%20on%20TV%20to%20distance%20himself%20from%20the%20suggestion%20while%20parliament%20was%20in%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20relied%20on%20reports%20published%20in%20two%20London%20newspapers%20alleging%20that%20the%20Adani%20group%20was%20using%20unsavoury%20foreign%20funding%20and%20round%20tripping%20of%20funds%20to%20further%20its%20businesses.%20These%20reports%20were%20sourced%20from%20the%20findings%20of%20Organised%20Crime%20%26amp%3B%20Corruption%20Reporting%20Project%20(OCCRP)%2C%20which%20is%20funded%20by%20billionaire%20George%20Soros%2C%20who%20has%20been%20labelled%20by%20a%20number%20of%20governments%20abroad%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Bagent%20of%20chaos%20and%20disruption%26quot%3B.%20This%20clearly%20was%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20gift%20to%20India%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20G20%20summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20alleged%20that%20the%20Adani%20group%2C%20which%20is%20involved%20in%20defence%20manufacturing%20besides%20infrastructure%20and%20green%20energy%2C%20had%20%26quot%3Bforeign%20links%26quot%3B%2C%20including%20with%20%26quot%3BChina%26quot%3B.%20The%20two%20foreign%20nationals%20he%20named%20are%20Nasser%20Ali%20Shaban%20Ahli%20from%20the%20UAE%20and%20Chang%20Chung-Ling%20from%20Taiwan%20-%20both%20nations%20have%20legitimate%20business%20ties%20with%20India%20and%20none%20of%20them%20can%20be%20described%20as%20%26quot%3BChinese%26quot%3B.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20perhaps%20thinks%20the%20Indian%20media%20is%20gullible%2C%20incapable%20of%20distinguishing%20between%20Peoples%20Republic%20of%20China%20and%20Taiwan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20allegations%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20sought%20to%20level%20%26quot%3Bde%20novo%26quot%3B%20have%20been%20probed%20and%20dismissed%20by%20India's%20democratically%20constituted%20institutions%20-%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%20(SEBI)%2C%20Enforcement%20Directorate(ED)%2C%20and%20the%20Department%20of%20Revenue%20Intelligence(DRI)%2C%20since%20they%20first%20surfaced%20with%20the%20publication%20of%20the%20Hindenburg%20report%20on%20January%2024%20(%20endorsed%2C%20cascaded%20by%20Soros%20in%20February).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20shouts%20from%20rooftops%20in%20India%20and%20abroad%20about%20disrespect%20shown%20to%20India's%20institutions%2C%20the%20rejection%20of%20the%20Hindenburg%20allegations%20by%20these%20very%20institutions%20is%20disregarded%20by%20him.%20Recent%20reports%20have%20shown%20that%20as%20a%20result%20of%20Hindenburg%2C%20short-sellers%20benefitted%20while%20Indian%20stocks%20crashed.%20Eighteen%20entities%20are%20being%20probed%20by%20ED%20and%20tax%20authorities%20on%20this%20score%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20findings%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court-appointed%20Justice%20AM%20Sapre%20panel%20and%20SEBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndira%20Gandhi%20was%20perennially%20wary%20of%20a%20%26quot%3BForeign%20Hand%26quot%3B%3B%20she%20feared%20that%20foreign%20entities%20in%20the%20West%2C%20chagrined%20by%20the%20success%20of%20the%20growth%20of%20democracy%20in%20India%20in%20spite%20of%20their%20persistent%20doomsday%20predictions%2C%20were%20out%20to%20destabilise%20the%20elected%20government%20of%20this%20land.%20Ironically%2C%20her%20grandson%20has%20chosen%20to%20outsource%2C%20or%20perhaps%20%26quot%3Bout-Soros%26quot%3B%2C%20his%20attack%20on%20Narendra%20Modi%20to%20questionable%20entities%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoros'%20credentials%20have%20been%20decried%20by%20Russia%2C%20Malaysia%2C%20South%20Korea%2C%20Indonesia%20and%20even%20European%20Union%20(EU).%20Malaysia's%20former%20president%20Mahathir%20Mohammed%2C%20who%20survived%20Soros'%20machinations%2C%20which%20triggered%20the%201997%20South%20East%20Asian%20economic%20crisis%2C%20described%20him%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bmoron%26quot%3B.%20The%20then%20rulers%20of%20South%20Korea%20and%20Indonesia's%20Suharto%20were%20not%20fortunate%20as%20Mahathir%20-their%20regimes%20were%20ousted.%20Soros'%20hand%20was%20evident%20in%20the%20Arab%20Spring%20in%20the%20early%202010s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoros%20is%20also%20known%20as%20the%20man%20who%20%26quot%3Bbroke%20the%20Bank%20of%20England%26quot%3B.%20His%20hedging%20earned%20him%20over%20a%20billion%20US%20Dollars%20while%20the%20British%20Pound%20went%20for%20a%20toss%20during%20the%201992%20Black%20Wednesday%20UK%20currency%20crisis.%20Though%20he%20has%20denied%20it%2C%20the%20Canadian%20organisation%20Adbusters%2C%20which%20was%20associated%20with%20the%20Wall%20Street%20demonstrations%20in%20the%20US%20in%202011%2C%20is%20suspected%20(per%20findings%20of%20Reuters)%20to%20be%20beneficiary%20of%20his%20%26quot%3Bphilanthropy%26quot%3B.%20Ahead%20of%20the%202024%20election%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20fondness%20for%20the%20man%20who%20destabilised%2C%20or%20tried%20to%20destabilise%20governments%20and%20economies%20tends%20to%20raise%20eyebrows.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20addressing%20the%20World%20Economic%20Forum%20(WEF)%20in%20Davos%20in%202020%2C%20George%20Soros%20spoke%20against%20rising%20nationalism%2C%20which%20he%20perceived%20as%20a%20threat.%20He%20mentioned%20three%20world%20leaders%20specifically%3A%20Xi%20Jinping%2C%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20and%20offered%20to%20fund%20a%20campaign%20against%20%26quot%3Bgrowing%20nationalism%26quot%3B%20with%20a%20corpus%20of%20%24%201%20billion%20to%20set%20up%20universities%20across%20the%20globe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20mentioned%20the%20political%20ramifications%20of%20the%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20allegations%2C%20and%20their%20rather%20questionable%20sourcing%2C%20let%20us%20analyse%20them%20one%20by%20one%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EFunds%20sent%20abroad%20by%20over-invoicing%20and%20the%20same%20money%20used%20to%20drive%20stock%20prices%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20fact%20is%20that%20DRI%20issued%20showcause%20notice%20in%202014%3B%20upon%20investigation%2C%20DRI%20found%20that%20all%20the%20imports%20were%20genuine%2C%20were%20undertaken%20at%20an%20arm's%20length%20and%20concluded%20that%20the%20value%20declared%20was%20correct%20and%20therefore%20there%20was%20no%20over-invoicing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EThere%20was%20a%20breach%20of%20the%20minimum%20public%20shareholding%20requirement%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court-appointed%20expert%20committee%20(Justice%20Sapre%20panel)%20examined%20the%20issue%20and%20found%20nothing%20of%20that%20sort%20happened.%20The%20committee%20did%20not%20find%20any%20violation%20of%20the%20requirement.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EThere%20was%20price%20manipulation%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Sapre%20committee%20said%20that%20there%20is%20no%20evidence%20to%20conclude%20that%20there%20has%20been%20price%20manipulation.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20the%20crux%20of%20the%20allegation%2C%20that%20Indian%20money%20went%20abroad%2C%20came%20back%20through%20offshore%20entities%20and%20led%20to%20unprecedented%20rise%20in%20share%20prices%2C%20does%20not%20hold%20water.%20These%20allegations%20have%20been%20rejected%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20recent%20days%2C%20as%20were%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20allegations%20on%20the%20Rafael%20deal%20and%20the%20Pegasus%20spyware%20scam%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20favourite%20jab%2C%26quot%3B%20crony%20capitalism%26quot%3B%2C%20this%20terminology%20gained%20currency%20in%201980%20(in%20the%20post%20Sanjay%20Gandhi%20era)%20when%20rules%20were%20bent%20to%20award%20a%20contract%20which%20favoured%20an%20Italian%20entity%2C%20represented%20over%20many%20decades%20in%20India%20by%20Ottavio%20Quattrocchi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20report%20of%20the%20Estimates%20Committee%20of%20Parliament%20of%20the%207th%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20which%20went%20into%20a%20deal%20of%20Rashtriya%20Chemicals%20%26amp%3B%20Fertilisers%20Ltd%20(%20known%20as%20Thal%20Vaishet%20deal)%2C%20had%20an%20interesting%20statement%20by%20then%20Chemicals%20%26amp%3B%20Fertilisers%20Secretary%20KV%20Ramanathan.%20A%20distinguished%20bureaucrat%2C%20he%20was%20bypassed%20for%20promotion%20as%20Cabinet%20Secretary%20in%201985%2C%20perhaps%20because%20of%20this%20statement.%20The%20parliamentary%20panel%20report%20records%20that%20MPs%20enquired%20why%20there%20had%20been%20a%20cost%20escalation%3B%20Ramnathan%20replied%20that%20it%20was%20necessitated%20by%20a%20last%20minute%20change%20in%20the%20vendor.%20Questioned%20by%20MPs%20if%20the%20last%20minute%20change%20was%20due%20to%20superior%20technical%20advice%2C%20the%20Secretary%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BNo%2C%20sir.%20The%20change%20was%20necessitated%20due%20to%20what%20I%20may%20term%20as%20superior%20extra-technical%20considerations%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThal%20Vaishet%20marked%20the%20rise%20of%20Quattrocchi.%20He%20quietly%20left%20the%20shores%20of%20India%20amid%20Bofors%20allegations%20in%201991.%20Attempts%20by%20the%20CBI%20to%20bring%20him%20before%20Indian%20courts%20failed.%20His%20death%20closed%20the%20chapter.%20Instances%20of%20cronyism%20and%20people%20wanted%20by%20the%20Indian%20courts%20disappearing%20to%20sanctuaries%20overseas%20has%20a%20history%20spanning%20over%20four%20decades.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20war%20cry%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3Echowkidar%20chor%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%20did%20not%20resonate%20with%20voters.%20During%20his%20impressive%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20said%20he%20was%20running%20a%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EMohabbat%20ki%20dukan%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B.%20His%20press%20interaction%20on%20Thursday%2C%20August%2031%2C%20showed%20the%20wares%20displayed%20in%20his%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3Edukaan%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%20in%20somewhat%20poor%20light.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Shubhabrata%20Bhattacharya%20is%20a%20retired%20Editor%20and%20a%20public%20affairs%20commentator)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693546680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fvgpani68_rahul-gandhi-pti-_625x300_07_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fnow-rahul-gandhi-outsoros-es-his-attack-on-narendra-modi-4347318%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20Thursday%2C%20August%2031%2C%20while%2063%20leaders%20of%2028%20parties%20who%20constitute%20the%20organisation%20with%20the%20moniker%20%26quot%3BIndian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance%26quot%3B%20(INDIA)%20prepared%20for%20their%20two-day%20meet%20in%20India's%20financial%20capital%2C%20Mumbai.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fnow-rahul-gandhi-outsoros-es-his-attack-on-narendra-modi-4347318%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fnow-rahul-gandhi-outsoros-es-his-attack-on-narendra-modi-4347318%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fnow-rahul-gandhi-outsoros-es-his-attack-on-narendra-modi-4347318%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B