p_articleshow%2F103269615.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22On%20Diamond%20League%20Second%20Place%20Finish%2C%20Neeraj%20Chopra's%20Honest%20Admission%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENewly-crowned%20world%20champion%20Neeraj%20Chopra%20missed%20out%20on%20a%20top%20podium%20finish%20to%20settle%20for%20second%20position%20with%20a%20final%20round%20throw%20of%2085.71%20metres%20in%20the%20men's%20javelin%20event%20of%20the%20Diamond%20League%20Meeting%20here.%20The%2025-year-old%20Chopra%2C%20also%20the%20reigning%20Olympic%20champion%2C%20produced%20three%20legal%20throws%20of%2080.79m%2C%2085.22m%20and%2085.71m%20while%20the%20remaining%20three%20were%20fouls.%20He%20finished%20behind%20Jakub%20Vadlejch%20(85.86m)%20of%20Czech%20Republic%2C%20who%20had%20won%20a%20bronze%20in%20the%20World%20Championships.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20champion%20thrower%20said%20after%20the%20event%20on%20Thursday%20that%20physically%20was%20feeling%20%26quot%3Bvery%20good%26quot%3B%20but%20was%20a%20little%20tired%20after%20the%20World%20Championships%20in%20Budapest%2C%20where%20he%20won%20gold.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20feel%20very%20good%20now%2C%20because%20everyone%20is%20a%20little%20tired%20after%20the%20World%20Championships.%20We%20gave%20our%20100%20per%20cent%20there%20(in%20Budapest)%2C%20but%20for%20this%20competition%20here%20my%20focus%20was%20to%20just%20stay%20healthy%2C%20and%20we%20have%20to%20focus%20now%20for%20Eugene%20(Diamond%20League%20finals%20on%20September%2017)%20and%20then%20the%20(Hangzhou)%20Asian%20Games%20(from%20September%2023).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20superstar%2C%20who%20was%20unbeaten%20this%20season%20before%20Thursday%2C%20qualified%20for%20the%20Diamond%20League%20finals%20in%20Eugene%2C%20USA%2C%20with%2023%20points%20from%20three%20meets.%20He%20had%20won%20the%20Diamond%20League%20trophy%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChopra%20has%20qualified%20for%20Diamond%20League%20finals%20at%20third%20spot%20behind%20Jakub%20Vadlejch%20(29%20points)%20and%20Julian%20Weber%20(25%20points).%20The%20Indian%20was%20third%20because%20he%20missed%20the%20Monaco%20leg%20of%20the%20Diamond%20League%20due%20to%20injury%20concerns%2C%20while%20Jakub%20and%20Weber%20participated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChopra%20had%20won%20the%20Diamond%20League%20meetings%20in%20Doha%20(May%205)%20and%20Lausanne%20(June%2030)%20--%20his%20only%20two%20competitions%20before%20winning%20a%20historic%20gold%20in%20the%20World%20Championships%20in%20Budapest%20on%20Sunday%20with%20a%20throw%20of%2088.17m.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Tokyo%20Olympics%20gold%20medallist%20indicated%20he%20didn't%20exert%20himself%20too%20much%20in%20Zurich%20order%20to%20be%20able%20to%20give%20his%20cent%20percent%20in%20the%20upcoming%20competitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20pre-event%20press%20conference%20here%2C%20Chopra%20had%20said%20that%20he%20was%20feeling%20a%20bit%20of%20pain%20on%20his%20shoulder%20and%20back%20after%20winning%20gold%20in%20the%20World%20Championships.%20He%20was%20not%20100%20per%20cent%20fit%20during%20the%20showpiece%20event%20due%20to%20a%20groin%20strain%20he%20had%20sustained%20while%20training%20in%20May-June.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20me%2C%20the%20focus%20was%20just%20to%20stay%20healthy%20and%20to%20give%20my%20100%20per%20cent%20in%20my%20next%20competitions.%20Sometimes%20we%20need%20to%20read%20our%20body.%20Today%2C%20I%20feel%20OK%2C%20I%20am%20100%20per%20cent%20OK%2C%20but%20I%20did%20not%20push%20too%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSometimes%2C%20our%20number%20one%20goal%20is%20to%20stay%20healthy.%20Today%2C%20I%20gave%20it%20my%20best%20but%20still%20with%20the%20focus%20to%20stay%20healthy.%20I%20usually%20do%20my%20winter%20training%20in%20Europe%2C%20because%20it%20is%20a%20lot%20easier%20to%20travel%2C%20that's%20why%20I%20spent%20some%20time%20in%20Loughborough%20(England)%20for%20some%20months%20before%20competing%20in%20Budapest%20this%20summer%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20Chopra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChopra%20began%20with%20a%20modest%2080.79m%20throw%20here%2C%20which%20put%20him%20in%20the%20second%20spot%20but%20he%20fouled%20the%20next%20two%20throws%20to%20slip%20to%20fifth%20at%20the%20halfway%20stage%20when%20Germany's%20Julian%20Weber%20was%20leading.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Chopra%20pulled%20off%2085.22m%20in%20his%20fourth%20attempt%20which%20saw%20him%20rise%20to%20second.%20By%20that%20time%2C%20Vadlejch%20had%20taken%20the%20lead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChopra%20fouled%20his%20fifth%20throw%20again%20but%20achieved%20his%20best%20of%20the%20day%20--%2085.71m%20--%20in%20his%20last%20throw.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChopra's%20next%20target%20would%20be%20to%20lift%20the%20Diamond%20League%20champion's%20trophy%20in%20Eugene%20on%20September%2017.%20He%20had%20won%20the%20trophy%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20Diamond%20League%20final%20will%20be%20a%20winner-takes-all%20affair%20with%20no%20points%20being%20carried%20forward%20from%20the%20Diamond%20League%20legs%20this%20season.%20There%20are%20four%20Diamond%20League%20individual%20legs%20before%20finals%20in%20each%20event%2C%20with%20the%20prize%20money%20different%20for%20each%20leg%20and%20the%20finals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChopra%20got%20US%20USD%206%2C000%20for%20his%20efforts%20in%20Zurich%2C%20while%20the%20winner%20earned%20US%20USD%2012%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20six%20qualify%20for%20finals%20in%20field%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20winner%20in%20the%20finals%20at%20Eugene%20will%20be%20richer%20by%20USD%2030%2C000%2C%20while%20the%20runner-up%20and%20third-place%20finishers%20will%20earn%20USD%2012000%20and%20USD%207000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20men's%20long%20jump%2C%20Murali%20Sreeshankar%20finished%20fifth%20here%20with%20a%20first-round%20jump%20of%207.99m.%20He%20also%20qualified%20for%20the%20Diamond%20League%20finals%20in%20third%20place%20on%20the%20standings%20with%2014%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESreeshankar%2C%20who%20h