20a%20show-cause%20notice%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20(TDP)%20chief%20and%20former%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20chief%20minister%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%2C%20asking%20why%20tax%20proceedings%20should%20not%20be%20initiated%20against%20him%20for%20having%20%E2%80%9Cundisclosed%20income%20%E2%80%9C%20of%20Rs%20118%20crore%20received%20as%20kickbacks%20from%20some%20infrastructure%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20notice%20was%20issued%20in%20response%20to%20Naidu%E2%80%99s%20preliminary%20objections%20that%20the%20tax%20proceedings%20against%20him%20could%20not%20have%20been%20initiated%20before%20the%20jurisdictional%20assessing%20officer%20undertook%20the%20exercise%20of%20reassessment%20of%20his%20income%20for%20the%20impugned%20financial%20years%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fincome-tax-department-issues-show-cause-notice-to-chandrababu-naidu-for-alleged-kickbacks-worth-118-crore-101693507669903.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnce%20the%20case%20is%20notified%20to%20this%20office%20(Central%20Circle)%2C%20immediately%20to%20commence%20the%20proceedings%2C%20notice%20under%20section%20153C%20was%20validly%20issued%20and%20the%20proceedings%20are%20in%20progress%2C%E2%80%9D%20stated%20the%20show-cause%20notice%2C%20adding%20the%20department%20has%20evidence%20to%20show%20that%20unaccounted%20income%20generated%20through%20bogus%20sub-contracts%20was%20given%20to%20Naidu%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESection%20153C%20of%20the%20I-T%20Act%20allows%20the%20revenue%20department%20to%20proceed%20against%20a%20party%20other%20than%20the%20person%20who%20has%20been%20searched%2C%20if%20certain%20incriminating%20materials%20are%20found%20against%20that%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20investigations%20against%20Naidu%20began%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fincome-tax-department-issues-show-cause-notice-to-chandrababu-naidu-for-alleged-kickbacks-worth-118-crore-101693507669903.html%5C%22%3Esearches%20were%20carried%20out%20on%20the%20premise%20of%20one%20Manoj%20Vasudev%20Pardasany%3C%2Fa%3E%20(referred%20to%20as%20MVP%20in%20the%20notice)%20who%20was%20taking%20part%20in%20the%20tendering%20process%20in%20the%20state%20since%20December%202017%20on%20behalf%20of%20Shapoorji%20Pallonji%20%26amp%3B%20Co.%20Pvt%20Ltd%20(SPCL)%2C%20and%20at%20the%20premises%20of%20Pardasany%E2%80%99s%20associates%20in%20November%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20statements%2C%20Pardasany%20admitted%20to%20having%20arranged%20bogus%20contacts%20and%20work%20orders%20for%20siphoning%20off%20of%20funds%20by%20SPCL%20to%20generate%20cash%20through%20fake%20sub-contractor%20companies%2C%20the%20notice%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSeveral%20incriminating%20messages%2C%20chats%20and%20excel%20sheets%20have%20also%20been%20recovered%20from%20MVP%20and%20his%20associates%20during%20search%20operations%20which%20show%20siphoning%20off%20of%20funds%20and%20cash%20generation%20by%20several%20major%20infrastructure%20companies.%20Delivery%20of%20such%20cash%20to%20you%20(Naidu)%20has%20also%20been%20unearthed%20during%20the%20course%20of%20search%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fincome-tax-department-issues-show-cause-notice-to-chandrababu-naidu-for-alleged-kickbacks-worth-118-crore-101693507669903.html%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20notice%2C%20MVP%20contacted%20Naidu%E2%80%99s%20personal%20secretary%20P%20Srinivas%20in%20August%2C%202016%20(when%20Naidu%20was%20CM)%2C%20who%20asked%20him%20to%20arrange%20for%20funds%20for%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFrom%20the%20statements%20of%20MVP%20recorded%20on%20November%201%2C%202019%20and%20November%205%2C%202019%2C%20it%20has%20been%20found%20that%20funds%20were%20siphoned%20off%20from%20projects%20allocated%20to%20SP%20by%20the%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20Government%20without%20doing%20any%20actual%20work%E2%80%A6Apart%20from%20Shapoorji%20Pallonji%20(SP)%2C%20funds%20were%20also%20siphoned%20off%20from%20L%26amp%3BT%20and%20delivered%20for%20use%20by%20you%20through%20companies%20such%20as%20Phoenix%20Infra%20%26amp%3B%20Pour%20Trading%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20notice%20to%20Naidu%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20I-T%20Department%20totalled%20the%20money%20MVP%20allegedly%20siphoned%20off%20from%20various%20sub-contractor%20companies%20to%20pay%20Naidu%20and%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CPlease%20state%20as%20to%20why%20an%20amount%20of%20%E2%82%B9118%2C98%2C13%2C2071-%20for%20AY%202020-21%20should%20not%20be%20treated%20as%20your%20undisclosed%20income.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20notice%20has%20come%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20speculations%20of%20a%20possible%20alliance%20between%20TDP%20and%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3ETimes%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693545321000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F24143246%2Fnaidu.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fchandrababu-naidu-receives-notice-from-i-t-dept-over-undisclosed-income-of-rs-118-crore%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20investigations%20against%20Naidu%20began%20after%20searches%20were%20carried%20out%20on%20the%20premise%20of%20one%20Manoj%20Vasudev%20Pardasany%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fchandrababu-naidu-receives-notice-from-i-t-dept-over-undisclosed-income-of-rs-118-crore%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tollywood%20director%20Arun%20Roy%20diagnosed%20with%20cancer%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693545304000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103269154%2Cimgsize-17340.cms%22%2