e-thomas-new-financial-disclosure-flights-scotus-2023-8%5C%22%3Edetails%20all%20sorts%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20ties%20to%20Crow%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20justice's%20lawyer%20released%20a%20statement%20defending%20the%20home's%20sale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%202014%2C%20Harlan%20Crow%2C%20a%20longtime%20friend%20of%20Justice%20and%20Mrs.%20Thomas%2C%20visited%20Savannah%20with%20Justice%20Thomas%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.berkefarah.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F8%2F31%2Felliot-s-berke-releases-statement-on-behalf-of-client-justice-clarence-thomas-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Elliot%20S.%20Berke%20reads.%20%26quot%3BMr.%20Crow%20witnessed%20firsthand%20how%20the%20neighborhood%20was%20blighted%20and%20dangerous%20with%20derelicts%2C%20drug%20users%2C%20and%20junkies%2C%20notably%20in%20the%20house%20next%20to%20the%20Justice's%20mother%20and%20in%20the%20other%20houses%20on%20her%20street.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThomas%20joined%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%201991%2C%20meaning%20that%20in%202014%2C%20when%20his%20mother%20was%20still%20living%20in%20a%20neighborhood%20blighted%20and%20dangerous%20with%20derelicts%2C%20drug%20users%2C%20and%20junkies%2C%20he'd%20been%20one%20of%20the%20most%20powerful%20people%20in%20the%20country%20for%20more%20than%2022%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20went%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMr.%20Crow%20asked%20Justice%20Thomas%20what%20he%20intended%20to%20do%20with%20the%20home%20after%20his%20mother%20(who%20was%20in%20her%2080s%20at%20the%20time)%20passed%20away%2C%20and%20the%20Justice%20replied%20that%20he%20intended%20to%20have%20the%20property%20bulldozed%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20reads.%20%26quot%3BMr.%20Crow%20indicated%20he%20wanted%20to%20preserve%20the%20home%20for%20a%20possible%20museum%20and%20asked%20his%20team%20to%20review%20the%20idea%20of%20doing%20so.%20When%20he%20first%20raised%20the%20idea%20of%20purchasing%