nd%20make%20energy%20systems%20within%20the%20city%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcolorado-springs-used-5g-smart-city-2023-7%5C%22%3Ework%20smarter%20than%20before%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20R%C3%A9seau%20d'Energies%20de%20Wavre%2C%20or%20REW%2C%20plan%2C%20every%20public%20building%20in%20Wavre%20will%20have%20a%20smart%20meter%20installed%20that%20keeps%20track%20of%20power%20usage%20among%20key%20infrastructure%20elements.%20It%20will%20also%20enable%20a%20peer-to-peer%20energy-sharing%20model%20that%20helps%20businesses%20and%20organizations%20share%20energy%20depending%20on%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20REW%20initiative%2C%20in%20which%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-frequency-is-5g%5C%22%3E5G-enabled%20SIM%20card%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20be%20installed%20in%20each%20meter%2C%20will%20help%20the%20city%20develop%20a%20%26quot%3Bsmart%20grid.%26quot%3B%20On%20this%20smart%20grid%2C%20energy%20use%20can%20be%20constantly%20monitored%2C%20modeled%2C%20and%20predicted%20using%20real-time%20dashboards.%20This%20can%20help%20ensure%20lower%20and%20more-efficient%20power%20use%20by%20more%20effectively%20modeling%20when%20people%20should%20use%20that%20energy.%20A%205G%20connection%20enables%20this%20through%20the%20always-on%2C%20affordable%20mobile%20data%20the%20project%20uses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWavre%20isn't%20new%20to%20innovation%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20past%2010%20years%2C%20the%20city%20of%20Wavre%20has%20been%20fully%20committed%20to%20the%20digital%20transition%2C%26quot%3B%20Anne%20Masson%2C%20the%20mayor%20of%20Wavre%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BFor%20us%2C%20new%20technologies%20are%20an%20essential%20means%20of%20meeting%20the%20expectations%20of%20a%20rapidly%20changing%20world%20as%20well%20as%20the%20expectations%20of%20the%20players%20in%20the%20economy%2C%20health%2C%20tourism%2C%20and%20culture%20located%20in%20our%20territory