%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20shares%20that%20a%20harder%20concept%20for%20most%20people%20to%20understand%20was%20the%20way%20in%20which%20he%20chose%20to%20travel.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20question%20my%20friends%20and%20family%20posed%20at%20the%20time%20was%2C%20%E2%80%98why%20do%20this%20on%20foot%3F%E2%80%99%20The%20answer%20was%20simple.%20By%20walking%20to%20different%20places%2C%20I%20get%20a%20chance%20to%20have%20a%20closer%20look%20at%20my%20surroundings%20and%20truly%20enjoy%20them.%20When%20we%20travel%20by%20buses%20and%20cars%2C%20we%20only%20reach%20the%20destination%20and%20forget%20about%20the%20road%20leading%20up%20to%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20Yati%20explains.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAll%20the%20stops%20on%20his%20way%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYati%20started%20his%20first-ever%20walking%20expedition%20from%20Rishikesh%20to%20Kedarnath%2C%20covering%20over%20216%20km%20on%20foot%2C%20in%20September%202020.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20came%20back%20home%2C%20I%20was%20greeted%20with%20the%20warmest%20reception.%20My%20mother%20was%20certainly%20happy%20that%20I%20did%20not%20become%20a%20%3Cem%3Esanyasi%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20my%20father%20was%20proud%20of%20my%20achievements%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20expedition%20that%20Yati%20went%20on%20covered%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20but%20that%20trip%20was%20cut%20short%20as%20he%20sustained%20an%20injury%20along%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20these%20locations%2C%20Yati%20also%20explored%20northeast%20India%2C%20mainly%20Sikkim%2C%20as%20his%20fourth%20expedition.%20Buttercup%20could%20not%20accompany%20him%20then%20as%20she%20was%20still%20a%20puppy%20and%20needed%20training.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20saw%20that%20Buttercup%20was%20old%20enough%20to%20accompany%20me%20for%20my%20fifth%20expedition%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20train%20her.%20We%20started%20with%20small%20walks