%20foot%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20his%20longest%20walks%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F310963%2Fsashi-bahuguna-raturi-uttarakhand-pisyu-loon-salt-namakwali-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eyet%20from%20Uttarakhand%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Kerala%20covering%20the%20four%20holy%20sites%20of%20India%20%E2%80%94%20Badrinath%2C%20Dwarka%2C%20Jagannath%20Puri%20and%20Rameswaram%20%E2%80%94%20Yati%20is%20excited%20about%20what%20is%20before%20them.%20He%20says%20that%20it%20will%20take%20him%20another%2010%20months%20to%20complete%20his%20Chardham%20expedition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20explore%20further%20down%20south%20and%20see%20the%20variety%20of%20cultures%20there.%20I%20have%20enjoyed%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Eevery%20bit%20of%20my%20walk%20so%20far%20and%20Buttercup%2C%20too%2C%20has%20been%20very%20enthusiastic%20about%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20an%20anecdote%20when%20he%20was%20met%20with%20kindness%20on%20the%20road%2C%20Yati%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20warned%20about%20language%20barriers%20in%20the%20southern%20part%20of%20the%20country.%20However%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20learn%20Telugu%20when%20I%20entered%20Andhra.%20In%20my%20broken%20Telugu%20in%20Visakhapatnam%2C%20I%20tried%20to%20explain%20to%20a%20shopkeeper%20how%20my%20parcel%20would%20be%20delivered%20here.%20He%20laughed%20and%20uttered%20broken%20Hindi%20so%20that%20it%20was%20easier%20for%20me%20to%20understand.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20he%20manages%20his%20travel%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fyati-2-1693402469.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Yati%20has%20travelled%20to%20states%20like%20Uttara