s%20I%20can%20with%20minimal%20clothing%20and%20essentials%20like%20medicines%20and%20toiletries.%20I%20also%20try%20to%20avoid%20using%20gadgets%20while%20walking%20to%20save%20as%20much%20battery%20as%20I%20can%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCwSVkTPhq60%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCwSVkTPhq60%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCwSVkTPhq60%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Yati%20Gaur%20(%40theunfoldingplay)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EReflecting%20on%20his%20journey%20so%20far%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CMany%20people%20I%20come%20across%20during%20my%20journeys%20inquire%20about%20the%20reason%20behind%20these%20walks.%20It%20seems%20people%20generally%20think%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20grand%20plan%20behind%20every%20action%20we%20take.%20But%20you%20know%20what%3F%20To%20me%2C%20life%E2%80%99s%20purpose%20is%20just%2C%20well%2C%20to%20live.%20I%20lucked%20out%20being%20born%20in%20a%20country%20that%E2%80%99s%20got%20it%20all%20%E2%80%93%20mountains%2C%20deserts%2C%20seas%2C%20oceans%20%E2%80%93%20you%20name%20it.%20My%20only%20wish%20is%20to%20feast%20my%20eyes%20on%20them.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20the%20initial%20reaction%20of%20his%20friends%20and%20family%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CEveryone%20thought%20that%20I%20had%20lost%20my%20mind%20and%20were%20pretty%20sure%20that%20I%20would%20quit%20after%20two%20days%20of%20walking.%20But%2C%20I%20did%20it.%20I%20walked%20for%208%20days%20and%20reached%20Kedarnath.%20The%20feeling%20is%20indescribable%20as%20I%20was%20so%20overwhelmed%20by%20what%20I%20had%20achieved.%20I%20knew%20then%20that%20I%20would%20not%20stop%20now.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYati%20has%20also%20been%20documenting%20his%20journey%20on%20Instagram%20and%20has%20an%20earnest%20following%20of%2053%2C319%20thousand%20people.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20have%20been%20loving%20our%20journey%20together%20and%20some%20brands%20have%20been%20generous%20enough%20to%20sponsor%20us.%20There%20is%20a%20UP-based%20gentleman%20who%20sponsored%20Buttercup%E2%80%99s%20food%20for%20the%20Chardham%20journey%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20childhood%20we%20have%20all%20heard%20our%20fathers%20and%20grandfathers%20brag%20and%20say%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Eduniya%20dekhi%20hai%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fem%3E(I%20have%20seen%20the%20world)%2C%20well%2C%20with%20such%20diversity%20in%20India%2C%20they%20might%20have%20just%20peeked%20through%20the%20keyhole%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20door.%20However%2C%20not%20for%20Yati%2C%20as%20he%20and%20Buttercup%20have%20literally%20been%20seeing%20the%20world%2C%20one%20town%20at%20a%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693404383000%2C%22visual%2